Comment: 0,1:02:42.46,1:02:45.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An waits patiently and full of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:08.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,My first errand. Summer adventure special.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:17.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the Seto Inland Sea we find the second biggest island next to Awaji island
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the first errand will take place on Shōdo island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:27.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The film "Twenty-four eyes" takes place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:34.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they made the film there they've opened up the filmset for tourists to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:38.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This will be the goal for the first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:43.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's about a young female teacher and 12 first-year students
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:48.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and how she reaches the hearts of those students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:01:07.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The teacher would ride her bicycle all the way round the sea shore and through the town to school on the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:13.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That the errand would follow a similar objective was conceived by the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:20.22,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578.908,227.091)\fs40}Kairi \N 3 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:17.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With the 3 year old Kairi who can greet people with a confident voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:22.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can also hand customers their voucher. \N "He can do the errand if it's in the movie set" is what his dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But as expected he can't go by bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(201.636,51.455)}He still can't ride one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:31.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since it takes 30 minutes with the bus how would he get there is what the father worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But they found a clue in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:47.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When the teacher hurt herself she returned to the town by boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:55.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The exact same route as the teacher sailed is open every spring holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sailing time is merely 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:08.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kairi's first errand will fall on the second week of April on a Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,Wonder if he can do it by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:14.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now finally it's that morning. Kairi's mother will ask him to help out with an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me with cleaning? \N Open the sliding doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:25.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before putting him to the task his mother wants to put him a "helping mode" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:31.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's not going too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up wipe the table. Yes, that's it. \NYou are really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:43.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is he really helpful? It seems like there is no chance of him going on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,No motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:48.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that time a phone call from the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. \N I forgot the sales vouchers. \N What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He uses these vouchers to hand out to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kairi, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:03.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kairi often goes with his father on deliveries so he knows about the blue voucher book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:08.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was in a very easy place to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kairi? \N - Yup? Yup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have to use it for a delivery. \N - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need this when I go to the film set village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:22.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This voucher book is needed for when he goes to the film set village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- What will you do? \N - I will bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:31.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if he says that his finger is still inside his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that I made an apron for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I made an apron for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When his father makes deliveries he also wears an apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it for when Kairi goes on deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:46.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He made this apron so that Kairi could look up to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Benten Circle. The shop's name is written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kairi, can you wear it and drop by? \N - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he's supposed to be stoked about the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- I will be waiting for you. \N - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not a strong response from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's 700 m. from the house to the boat boarding dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:19.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will then deliver the vouchers to his father waiting in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,High five!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is he excited about going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,High five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Maybe not after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,He stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:38.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His sister cheered with her support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,She said "do your best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder if the feeling reached to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He started moving faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that the shop is called Benten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Blue Line!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Blue Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mom, there is a blue line. \N - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,See! Blue Line has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:09.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Blue line is the ferry that connects Shōdo island with Takamatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:16.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rather than being excited about helping his father he's excited about seeing the jumbo ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.32,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:28.02,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Blue Line. Bye bye and I will ride you once again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:33.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He suddenly changed into the usual big brother with a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:37.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kairi loves huge things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And of course he also loves busses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:45.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Carp streamers. \N Carp streamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:49.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are big. Just like that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:58.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, a real one is there. \N But it's in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:08.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if it's that far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:11.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, he sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:27.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can't move. \N But at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An old lady came out and started talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.76,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,A dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like them? Want me to walk down the street with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go? Okay then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Phew, what a help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.10,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you like cats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:53.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Cats. If only it was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:07:00.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if it scares him he makes sure to greet it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:04.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother has made a flag that says: "I will cross".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boat boarding station is on the other side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:12.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It takes about 10 minutes to the film set village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:20.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boarding stop is located at \Nolive beach which is 700 meters broad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:25.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Marine sports in the Seto Inland Sea take place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:33.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Going left here and he will be at the boarding stop. Seems like he knows the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's up with his facial expression?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:43.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It has departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.46,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,- No way. \N - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:50.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boat is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was requested to go the film set village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:58.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While it takes 10 minutes each way it takes time for the tourists to board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So it won't be heading back until after 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It has departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:07.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The harshness of the ocean as well as its kindness the 3 year old man who knows this well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,- So cool. \N - Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.01,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,Blue Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:18.49,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Blue Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:26.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like his father wanted. A confident boy who loves the ocean and its ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shōdo island where both the ocean and the mountains are near
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:36.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and where the temperature is closer to that of Spain or Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:40.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this island famed for its handmade soy sauce and sōmen noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:43.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it also produces the most amount of olives in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:48.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is what charms the tourists who visit the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Anpan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:55.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter how loud his singing is\N it bothers no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.55,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's coming. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boat is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:13.19,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! \N It came, it came!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What an energetic kid. \N - He's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, just as he has been asked to. \NGreeting people with a confident voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The usual fare is 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:31.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But if he tells them he wants to go to Benten Circle only for today it will be free to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I wish to go to Benten Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, he said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,To Benten Circle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I came to deliver something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:47.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since there are no other customers he was allowed to sit in the special seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:49.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,How lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The weather is so fine today and there's no wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:07.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The small boat is floating on top of the ocean that is clear as a mirror and heads towards the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,What an amazing view.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What a nice expression. \N - That's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:24.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Within 10 minutes and they can finally see the film set village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:26.47,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Carry me please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:31.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is able to properly ask for help. \N His height is only 91 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:35.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed that he forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.95,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Old man. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. He forgot to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,Such a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:47.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628.364,653.273)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(629.818,705.637)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:55.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the film set village for "Twenty-Four Eyes".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.47,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I came to deliver something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.455,651.818)}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,707.091)}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he came to deliver something \Nthere won't be any entrance fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:15.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the set that director of the color remake: Asama Yoshitaka used for the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:18.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder where dad is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:24.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The place that the father is always at is at a restaurant in a gallery called Kinema cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father delivers rice and vegetables to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father is supposedly in \Nthe warehouse furthest away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman went on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He knows that Kairi has arrived on the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:46.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Put his father plans on not coming out until his son calls him in a confident voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's just pretending to be doing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has to say: "This is a delivery".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he says nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:12:00.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Erika and Minami who always give \Nhim candy are right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.31,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Not here. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't he going to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:08.87,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,He wasn't there. I will go over there and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He could've just called for him. \N - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He will look for him elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seems like he knows where else to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:21.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But this place is instead where the gallery is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:27.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's looking for his father there. \N But his father is always back at that kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:42.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's totally not looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, what did you come here to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.16,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh? I came here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,He forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:53.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go and see if there are any fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:59.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He just passed the restaurant again and went straight to check up on his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, he went to look at the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Kobuchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kobuchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:08.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He calls Asian sheepshead wrasse for kobuchan. \NThe endearing nickname he uses while feeding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.73,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What? Kobuchan aren't coming at all. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:14.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.42,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Kobuchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:20.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile his father who has \N nothing better to do but to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,Like he is looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Kobuchan. Oh, it went over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The fish just doesn't let him approach them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.62,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will also check if dad is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,He finally remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:41.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has played enough for today. \N But he came here because of the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He returned to the restaurant his father is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.62,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I came to deliver something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's for Benten Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can finally hear Kairi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.86,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I came here for a delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(625.455,663.455)}Kairi, did you come by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:02.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602.182,708.545)}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.83,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You forgot this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The crucial voucher book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so well raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you did so well. \N Why don't you feed the fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Feed for the fish. \N Hey, the sheepshead wrasse are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:25.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It gulped it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you don't feed them then they won't come to you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:30.98,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Kobuchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The unchanging blue-green ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and at the foot of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:41.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are still 3 years until \N Kairi begins elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the world of movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I felt proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amazing that a 3 year old kid is riding a boat by himself. \N - Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way he thanked the old man in sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he was sitting there he expressed such satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And somebody in the studio even cried during that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Remembering when I was that age \Nand trying my best
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and when he clearly answered "I came here to play".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When going outside by yourself\N for the first time it can be quite scary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and there all these excitements and unknowns. \N It made me think of when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time Sugiyama has also \N put her child out on their first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel nervous and all kinds of weird feelings are mixed in while watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are worries such as whether they can succeed or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's very exciting to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to see your kids first errand later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama family's first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomiura is located in Chiba prefecture (Town of Minamibōsō).
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where we can find the father-daughter couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The cool daughter who loves her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki who is 3 years and 9 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.94,Studio,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The day her little brother - Doushi - was born she turned into a big sister overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:37.29,GreenFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(295.272,157.273)}Jinsei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love my father" is what she's been saying a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She will go on an errand for her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:46.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those are dad's legs and his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.545,666.364)}What about a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:54.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.091,712.909)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:57.34,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Won't do it, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,They have a great relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.66,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:06.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the mother told us. \NThe two of them are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:10.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rather than father and daughter \N they behave like a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The house her father grew up in is nearby. \N It's a guest house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:23.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Every morning the grandfather gets the fresh fish and prepares them for his customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mom, what can I help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.69,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you help out with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:36.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The truth is that since a couple of days they've been training Koiki to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:39.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today she will do whatever they tell her to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I will go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:45.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father will go with grandpa to collect the recent catches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take care. \N - Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He always enjoys the bento that his wife makes for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:55.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But this time he has forgotten it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Whose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An onigiri bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.54,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Is it dad's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:04.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki immediately noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is he still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father, hurry. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.43,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hurry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,Close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,He barely managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This will be the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He left, Koiki. \N What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so dejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave the house because of the electrician coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:28.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What will they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did dad go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.10,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows that he left for the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:42.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grandfathers boat is waiting 2 km away from their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:47.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It returns here for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For my first errand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did she figure out it's for the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No no no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:07.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Last month everyone in the neighborhood was praising her big brother saying: "Wow, you were able to go on your first errand".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:14.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up, I (Koiki) will go. \NIt's a true "first errand" fad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:20.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But there's one puzzling thing \Nin regards to Koiki's first errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:26.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother has given her a good luck charm with words of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:32.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pipi? (sounds of weeping)  \NIt's because Koiki tends to cry very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:43.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As soon as things don't go her way she will start weeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:48.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why her dad and her made their own word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki, pipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:54.87,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.55,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.38,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I won't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:02.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to be called a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wants to be seen as a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.01,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say here? \NIt's the word we use every time you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:26.58,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Pipi, I will not cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cry just look at this good luck charm, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at this and give it all you got. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, stand up. I will put it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will be fine if she's got this charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:48.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Aiming for the coast
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:52.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,her father will return to the harbor around noon for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.51,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.20,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:05.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today she departed the house without crying all pipi-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just as she promised her dad who she loves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Song lyrics: She has started walking with a charm in her chest that her mother put on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:24.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She uses all her strength to head for the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- You are so cute. \N - Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:36.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's no time for the abundance of greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though it's a street without a crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:47.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,since she's a big sister she knows how to properly cross a street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:47.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:55.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunch. I wonder if the boat is about to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.87,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The boat is returning to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(183.273,606.727)\fs20}Original song: \N By Keiko Utoku · Shingo Maekawa \N The loving words from the jet of a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:13.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've already caught lots of shellfish and have returned to the harbor to deliver them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:20.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they can hear her \N if she shouts in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:29.30,Studio,,0,0,0,,A sigh instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:31.46,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:34.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? She will not shout for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:36.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.89,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:46.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since her father is completely focused on getting the seashells out he has not noticed the Koiki is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:46.54,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:55.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter how long she's been standing there she's not shouting out to her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:59.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is she leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those people out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.55,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Dad and grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:06.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman couldn't help himself and spoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shout to them don't you think they will hear you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's careful since it's a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And she often says "can't do it" and then gives up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it will be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.64,0:23:24.18,Studio,,0,0,0,,Must be a bit embarrassing for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:26.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nothing came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:37.06,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy. Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:39.90,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy. Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:44.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, she shouted out to them. \N But they can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:51.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her voice didn't reach them but she won't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:56.65,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,One, two and... Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:59.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:06.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At 3 years and 9 months \Nthis is the loudest she has ever been in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:11.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her voice reached her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:14.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:24.51,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.08,0:24:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:31.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are like lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.73,0:24:33.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The affectionate bond between Koiki and her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.44,0:24:42.83,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,You forgot your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.49,0:24:48.07,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I came here to bring it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.06,0:24:53.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The voices of the two is flying across the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.54,0:24:59.14,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,O-Onigiri. You forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.13,0:25:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.08,0:25:03.94,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.06,0:25:04.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.33,0:25:07.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.091,666.364)}Koiki.. the harbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.37,0:25:07.27,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635.636,715.818)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.65,0:25:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.09,0:25:13.11,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.88,0:25:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, tears are starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.88,0:25:20.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,I get it. Of course they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:28.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because of how long they spent touchingly shouting at each other she had to wait an extra 12 minutes for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:34.97,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,- Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:34.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,- Did you come by yourself? How great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.96,0:25:37.31,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I came alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.89,0:25:44.62,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.091,666.364)}There's also grandpas lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.89,0:25:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.182,707.091)}You also brought mine? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.61,0:25:47.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.41,0:25:54.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Remembering the word pipi she didn't cry even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.65,0:25:59.55,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Dad, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.21,0:26:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I also love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.70,0:26:08.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's no room for grandpa in this equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.49,0:26:11.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Hey grandpa. \N - He looks so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.60,0:26:17.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because she excelled at this errand the father has thought up the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.86,0:26:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The filefish and turban shell that we just caught
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,can you bring them to Genbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.25,0:26:28.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki responds immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.40,0:26:35.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will have to bring them to the guesthouse at her fathers childhood home called Genbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.49,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.48,0:26:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See? They are right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.08,0:26:43.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The filefish that they caught this morning are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:46.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.36,0:26:48.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.10,0:26:49.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even turban shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.76,0:26:53.05,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's peeking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.04,0:26:56.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They caught 3 of each type.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.53,0:26:59.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's quite a heavy load. \N I wonder if it will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.93,0:27:00.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,- That's heavy. \N- Yeah, it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.45,0:27:05.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First she will go to the marketplace \Nand get them to add ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.14,0:27:10.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The guesthouse Genbei is further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.70,0:27:11.15,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.65,0:27:13.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.65,0:27:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki will you use this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.62,0:27:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.69,0:27:18.81,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What is a secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.06,0:27:22.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father got it from a hardware store just this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.81,0:27:29.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For 2950 yen. \N With this she can carry anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.61,0:27:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.61,0:27:30.89,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm heading off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.88,0:27:34.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father has been planning for this day for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.96,0:27:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best until you reach Genbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.84,0:27:40.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just hoping that this will be a good memory for Koiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.21,0:27:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You two love each other a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.86,0:27:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I still hold back on my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.81,0:27:47.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:51.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And about the expression of love that cost 2950 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.86,0:27:55.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki has taken it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.06,0:27:59.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since it is past noon calm has fallen over the marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.48,0:28:06.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her fathers senior at his middle school - \N Masayoshi - works there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.12,0:28:11.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've arranged that if she shouts \N "Masayoshi" then he will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.61,0:28:16.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she's a bit scared by her fathers senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.58,0:28:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he's a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.62,0:28:20.47,Studio,,0,0,0,,Too scary looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.74,0:28:24.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It might be due to him always talking in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.30,0:28:27.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder if Koiki will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.37,0:28:34.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's see if she will manage to \Ncall him in a confident voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.53,0:28:40.10,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Masayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.09,0:28:41.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.49,0:28:43.23,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I came on an errand by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.22,0:28:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An errand? To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.85,0:28:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself? \N How remarkable you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.94,0:28:52.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? He's a very kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.05,0:28:55.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like her father. Men of the sea \N are both strong and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:58.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Masayoshi has worked at the fish market for 26 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.82,0:29:03.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's working there as a general worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.46,0:29:04.81,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,There's some tape inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.80,0:29:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they prepared some tape for it. \NWhat will you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.58,0:29:10.35,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.34,0:29:11.55,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,To put some ice in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Put ice in it. Alright, I will put some in for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:18.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since it's after hours for the market\N he's been waiting all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:19.91,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.90,0:29:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.92,0:29:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:25.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's known her since she was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.80,0:29:27.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.21,0:29:40.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From just being thought of as a baby \N she is now regarded as a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:45.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to daddy's secret weapon carrying it would be easy-peasy is what they thought but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.82,0:29:49.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it's not that easy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:54.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Koiki who usually quits right away won't quit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.34,0:29:58.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She pulls with all her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.20,0:30:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She could've just used the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:05.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to pipi she won't cry or give up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:09.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,cause she is carrying her fathers catch of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.21,0:30:14.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the guesthouse Genbei. \N The house her father grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.32,0:30:20.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her dad told her that when she's at the entrance she should yell out: "Mom, please come and help."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.93,0:30:22.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, did she arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.42,0:30:26.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She noticed her but she has decided not to come out until she is being called.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.80,0:30:30.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's not calling for her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.68,0:30:32.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is she carrying it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.72,0:30:34.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She intends to bring it in all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.77,0:30:36.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:43.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has made sure to open the doors wide open\N but it's still heavy from all the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.18,0:30:53.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't get it over the last 10 cm of the last step.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.89,0:30:58.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though she could've gotten her mother to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.93,0:31:01.18,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:04.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she wants to do it by herself until the last step.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.56,0:31:04.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,How remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.90,0:31:09.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't quit now that she brought it all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.57,0:31:17.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Properly closing the screen doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.73,0:31:18.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.08,0:31:25.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with this the errand is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.52,0:31:24.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.00,0:31:27.29,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.84,0:31:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.96,0:31:32.87,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I brought it with me mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.86,0:31:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.36,0:31:38.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Turns out she's actually a really strong-willed kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.61,0:31:43.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the first time her mother has seen Koiki's face so full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.82,0:31:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.40,0:31:47.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.29,0:31:52.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the ice they managed to create an extremely fresh dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.53,0:31:54.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.70,0:31:59.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's enjoying it with such a prideful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.18,0:32:00.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.18,0:32:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.04,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Koiki, who will you marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.89,0:32:07.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:10.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what she always says.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.88,0:32:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.24,0:32:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This was truly a wonderful errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.46,0:32:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was truly an adorable dad and daughter couple and you seemed really touched when they called each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.70,0:32:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a trendy drama. \N They went "Koiki" and "daddy".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.04,0:32:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no room for grandpa in this duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.46,0:32:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed so dejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.74,0:32:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wants to eat with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.77,0:32:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,His face told the entire tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.44,0:32:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Imagine that dad on her wedding day. \N - Yeah, he will be crying big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- He will watch this video on that day. \N - No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.49,0:32:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you have a huge family, right? \N - Yes, I have 6 children.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.37,0:32:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The youngest one is 4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.64,0:32:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never put anyone out on an errand. So I'm amazed by how well raised the kids here are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.41,0:33:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the parents must train them well for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.24,0:33:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With Koiki I thought it was amazing how she brought the luggage in herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.21,0:33:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Her parents have clearly told her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.60,0:33:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"if you open something then close it."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.58,0:33:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and she did close it but there \Nwas still a small crack left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.41,0:33:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.10,0:33:23.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the vicinity of Sumida river we find high-rise buildings erected in the heart of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.41,0:33:30.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And as you enter the shopping street it starts smelling of Monjayaki like a true Edo part of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.70,0:33:34.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father brought a house in this desirable building before marrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:35.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then he fulfilled his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.96,0:33:38.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who was born here is Ryuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.22,0:33:41.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A stylish kid who will only wear the fanciest shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.22,0:33:44.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Looking good is a recent interest of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.74,0:33:45.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,He does look stylish
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.00,0:33:49.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today at Ryu's house a friend has come to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.73,0:33:52.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Soichiro who lives in a similar apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.81,0:33:56.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His favorite food is fatty tuna, herring roe and mitarashi rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.65,0:33:59.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother is born in Tsukijima (the famous fish market).
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.33,0:34:02.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu who gets things done and Sou who is more prudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.57,0:34:07.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are like axel and break so their mothers thought of an errand they could both go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.60,0:34:12.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But they live right next to the famous monjayaki street of Tsukushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.13,0:34:14.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everything can be found here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.04,0:34:16.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So they will be requested by Sou's grandma in Tsukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.88,0:34:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's a-chan so please sit here. \N - Who is a-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.10,0:34:21.65,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,My grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.64,0:34:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice. Is her house near?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.37,0:34:24.95,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Tsukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.94,0:34:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.50,0:34:31.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Crossing the Tsukuda bridge they will go to grandmas house to get some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.72,0:34:34.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Back over the bridge to get diapers for little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.94,0:34:38.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then getting yoghurt from the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.85,0:34:38.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,So difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.56,0:34:45.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu is the one wearing the strong yellow and the other one is Sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.90,0:34:47.54,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.53,0:34:50.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who knows the way to Tsukiji is Sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.25,0:34:53.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and the one who knows the way to the drug store is Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.10,0:34:56.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are going together they share the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.68,0:35:03.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To keep them from fighting the mothers made sure to only give them one bag that they have to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:06.53,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, I found a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.52,0:35:08.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who noticed is Sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.81,0:35:11.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please don't look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.08,0:35:12.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,- This is bad. \N - Don't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.60,0:35:13.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I found yet another camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.24,0:35:15.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is bad. We can't film like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.80,0:35:19.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's fine. In those situations...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.09,0:35:21.69,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(641.455,670.727)}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.09,0:35:21.69,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(645.818,712.909)}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.68,0:35:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for measuring electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.68,0:35:26.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They immediately lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.37,0:35:28.37,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Look at our matching rubber boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.36,0:35:30.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Proud of being stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.32,0:35:33.86,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Since I lent them to Ryuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.85,0:35:39.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if they have noticed the cameras they aren't aware that they are being filmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.79,0:35:42.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are only focused on one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.16,0:35:48.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Prior experiments with this filming style has taught us that it's possible to get away with until they are about 5 years and 3 months old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.79,0:35:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Errand. Errand. It's fun. \NSince it's fun then it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.60,0:36:02.47,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, another camera. \NGod day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.46,0:36:04.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if they see it no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.14,0:36:05.87,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Also measuring the electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.86,0:36:07.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Also measuring the electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.65,0:36:11.83,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, there too. An there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.82,0:36:12.75,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.74,0:36:15.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter how well hidden the boys spot them easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.57,0:36:17.31,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Many over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.30,0:36:19.21,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Are you counting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.29,0:36:20.38,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Getting peckish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.37,0:36:21.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.82,0:36:22.83,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.04,0:36:24.27,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Nice idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.26,0:36:31.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are good friends they share water bottle. \N They are thirsty from all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.67,0:36:34.96,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,You drink so gracefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.95,0:36:37.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's see a point from the cameramens guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.93,0:36:40.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"If they are asked then they should ask a new question."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.80,0:36:42.79,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.78,0:36:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.74,0:36:44.83,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,What kind of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.85,0:36:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:47.09,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.08,0:36:47.46,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.45,0:36:48.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The topic changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.58,0:36:50.29,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Going on an errand by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:51.83,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,The two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.82,0:36:55.42,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Because we were asked to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.41,0:36:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.99,0:36:59.80,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.79,0:37:01.53,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It smells good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:03.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.47,0:37:06.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've reached this far without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:10.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have neared Kachidoki bridge which is near their grandmothers house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:16.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Both are born between January and April 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.11,0:37:20.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They often fight about who is in the wrong and pass the blame to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.51,0:37:24.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when they turned 4 they suddenly stopped fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.15,0:37:30.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have found a way to reconcile and become good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.14,0:37:31.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.34,0:37:33.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grandmas house is just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.28,0:37:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this happen in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.13,0:37:39.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who is at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.56,0:37:40.57,Studio,,0,0,0,,Are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.14,0:37:43.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's watch it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.50,0:37:45.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Does this happen in real life?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.76,0:37:53.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, will they fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.00,0:37:52.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,Equally to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.66,0:37:55.49,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.48,0:37:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.83,0:37:57.62,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.68,0:37:58.45,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.48,0:38:01.25,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Hurt, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.24,0:38:05.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So this is how they've avoided fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.51,0:38:07.52,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Here? Is it much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.19,0:38:10.49,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.48,0:38:11.86,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.46,0:38:14.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Arrival at grandmas house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.36,0:38:18.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She lives on the first floor so they need to hit the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.03,0:38:23.27,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I came all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.20,0:38:24.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,But they both came.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.54,0:38:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, So.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.74,0:38:27.83,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I came with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:31.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He let his friend go first. \N"Please go first."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.78,0:38:35.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And he heads straight for the house altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.44,0:38:43.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu is well-brought up. When visiting a house he prays at their altar. I'm sure his friends' ancestors will be pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:46.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sounds are a bit odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.44,0:38:47.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,The other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.61,0:38:50.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's using the wrong end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.65,0:38:55.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The grandmother starts to pack \Nthe best parts of the fish that she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.86,0:38:57.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This fish is definitely delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.68,0:38:58.95,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Lend me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.94,0:39:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ryu's camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.28,0:39:01.67,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.66,0:39:05.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They need a picture to prove that they did the errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.31,0:39:07.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu took it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.06,0:39:10.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This picture will prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.19,0:39:11.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's making a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.16,0:39:12.93,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We've walked so much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.92,0:39:13.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.90,0:39:15.99,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm getting kind of tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.98,0:39:21.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tired? There's still more to go. \NBoth the drug store and supermarket are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.06,0:39:21.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.05,0:39:22.52,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's buy some juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.51,0:39:23.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu who acts on his impulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.01,0:39:26.04,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We'll use up all our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:28.30,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,That's no good. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.29,0:39:29.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.22,0:39:31.14,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go play in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:31.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.91,0:39:33.32,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.31,0:39:34.51,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:35.83,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.85,0:39:37.43,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.42,0:39:38.09,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.08,0:39:39.17,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.16,0:39:40.17,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.16,0:39:42.37,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We will be scolded by our mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.87,0:39:43.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,You will be scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.36,0:39:44.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The prudent Sou puts a stop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.92,0:39:46.34,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.33,0:39:47.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will they fight each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.77,0:39:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.27,0:40:00.71,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:03.23,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,No thanks. We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.22,0:40:04.73,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.72,0:40:05.45,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.44,0:40:06.57,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.56,0:40:07.57,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.56,0:40:09.70,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We will be scolded by our mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.72,0:40:12.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The prudent Sou puts a stop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.27,0:40:13.54,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.53,0:40:15.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will they fight each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.34,0:40:16.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.01,0:40:20.82,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Swing swing goes the swing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.13,0:40:20.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is what they've started doing to avoid fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.27,0:40:23.24,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,This is Kachidoki bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.09,0:40:28.49,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ka●chi●do●ki bridge is what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:26.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,So he can read?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:32.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This isn't the route their mothers suggested but it's even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.76,0:40:37.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They just have to cross the bridge and head for Tsukishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.13,0:40:40.15,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's take a commemorative photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.14,0:40:43.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now they can remember walking back on Kachidoki bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.56,0:40:45.45,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,What an amazing scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.44,0:40:47.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will they remember the trip by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.59,0:40:54.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Crossing the bridge is a first for both of them\N and yet they didn't take a picture of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.28,0:40:55.45,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We've crossed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.52,0:40:57.31,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's take another picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.30,0:41:00.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Take a picture of the plaque. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.78,0:41:03.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They can't read kanji yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.78,0:41:03.27,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:05.35,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Then it's better not to take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.34,0:41:09.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They won't take a picture since they can't read the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.87,0:41:09.29,Studio,,0,0,0,,They don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.28,0:41:12.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've returned to the monjayaki street of Tsukishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.43,0:41:14.63,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,It might be sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.62,0:41:18.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are heading for the drugs store a block from Ryu's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.49,0:41:19.52,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Ryuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.51,0:41:20.28,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.27,0:41:22.02,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Is our house this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:23.86,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,See? We've reached our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.85,0:41:24.90,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.89,0:41:28.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But which direction should they go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.16,0:41:30.01,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Where is Papasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.00,0:41:32.37,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's find someone so ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:36.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They asked the cameraman who has been stationed in front of their apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.33,0:41:38.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This shop has been here in 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.59,0:41:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Papasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.42,0:41:41.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Papasu on the other hand is a new shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.43,0:41:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.44,0:41:43.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.56,0:41:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.91,0:41:46.29,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We are on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.28,0:41:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.29,0:41:50.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady knows both the old and new shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.61,0:41:52.28,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, Papasu is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.27,0:41:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there so you have to cross at the crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.21,0:41:56.74,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.21,0:41:56.74,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Papasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.73,0:41:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can? It's just over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.86,0:42:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.86,0:42:00.00,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.99,0:42:00.93,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.92,0:42:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.92,0:42:02.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Helpful instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.94,0:42:04.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She swiftly went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.28,0:42:07.85,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.84,0:42:09.01,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.00,0:42:14.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are bying diapers for their little brothers. \N Medium for Sou and Big size for Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.66,0:42:17.37,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,707.091)}We want M, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.66,0:42:17.37,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(277.818,705.636)}I want M.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.36,0:42:19.06,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's go with M.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.05,0:42:22.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's following Ryu's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.18,0:42:23.96,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Where are there more diapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.95,0:42:26.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's never had to purchase diapers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.67,0:42:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,M? L?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.26,0:42:31.46,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Which one was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.45,0:42:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The big ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.45,0:42:34.69,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I was told to get the big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.02,0:42:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.33,0:42:37.62,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Big?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.61,0:42:39.26,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.25,0:42:42.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Big. That was a bit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Errand                        errand                        how jolly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.86,0:42:58.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They didn't fight even once so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.08,0:43:00.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only yoghurt is remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.70,0:43:03.97,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,What are we getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.96,0:43:07.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The yoghurt they want is placed on a high shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.48,0:43:08.60,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Can we grab it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.16,0:43:11.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu is 105 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.59,0:43:12.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.75,0:43:14.11,Studio,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.86,0:43:14.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.80,0:43:15.84,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I will grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.83,0:43:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sou is 5 cm shorter at a mere 100 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.46,0:43:19.51,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.07,0:43:20.15,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.52,0:43:29.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu steps up to the challenge. The two have learned to help each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.33,0:43:35.58,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.81,0:43:38.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,What an amazing feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.59,0:43:42.14,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We better hurry. Our mothers are waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.10,0:43:44.24,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.20,0:43:52.11,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.20,0:43:52.11,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,We walked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.25,0:43:56.20,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.19,0:44:01.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Crossing both Tsukuda and Kachidoki bridge. \N They've really made the rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:02.65,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,See. We've come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:04.07,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We really have.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.23,0:44:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.33,0:44:18.14,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a camera over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.81,0:44:19.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.13,0:44:20.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryu immediately finds the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.60,0:44:22.81,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Why are there cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.80,0:44:24.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The electricity company.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.35,0:44:26.74,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Electricity? Are they getting any reception?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.73,0:44:28.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.61,0:44:34.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,8 years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.13,0:44:38.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two are walking down Kachidoki bridge again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.41,0:44:42.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are first year students in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:48.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They go to different schools so even if they live close they don't have many opportunities to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.51,0:44:49.54,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.53,0:44:50.45,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.44,0:44:52.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking a picture this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.01,0:44:54.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder if they can read the sign this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.28,0:44:56.69,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Which side should I stand on?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.68,0:44:59.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ryuta has grown the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.26,0:45:03.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has grown to 172 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.18,0:45:06.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Souichirou might start growing from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.03,0:45:08.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've become like a comedic duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.70,0:45:11.46,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I can't get your face in frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.43,0:45:17.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Again? You can't tell where they are in this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.16,0:45:23.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are in Tsukishima they might as well eat some monjyayaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.56,0:45:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:26.25,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.24,0:45:28.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since this is the home town of Ryuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.64,0:45:32.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He prefers to do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.97,0:45:34.54,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Ooops, I spilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.99,0:45:36.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,Spilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.00,0:45:41.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,He can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.00,0:45:41.24,Studio,,0,0,0,,He can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.23,0:45:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta use oil first.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.20,0:45:44.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yep, oil first.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.36,0:45:46.21,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,You have no clue how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.00,0:45:51.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eh? He's pouring it from above?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.31,0:45:55.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then chop up the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.47,0:45:57.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is how it should be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.01,0:46:00.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Create a ring and pour the soup in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.83,0:46:02.62,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Pour it all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.61,0:46:04.53,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,This is how we always do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.56,0:46:06.43,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.42,0:46:08.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We need to reinforce the ring first.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.86,0:46:14.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. Have to wait for the ring to absorb the liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.30,0:46:20.69,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,It needs more time. It's still too soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.94,0:46:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Starting to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.75,0:46:24.65,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,What school club are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.64,0:46:25.60,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.59,0:46:27.92,WhiteYellowBorder,,0,0,0,,The club with the least amount of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.96,0:46:34.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While it's with fewer days here is Ryuta painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.21,0:46:38.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He loves mountains and sceneries.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.32,0:46:40.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about Souichiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.82,0:46:47.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From the age of 4 he's been going with his family every season. He's been excelling through even the harder trails.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.82,0:46:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325.818,414.727)\fs20}Little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.17,0:46:51.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The ski club has even fewer days.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.42,0:46:57.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've both selected the club with the least amount of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.07,0:47:01.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How is the taste of Tsukishima, Souichiro from Tsukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.64,0:47:02.85,RedFill,,0,0,0,,Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.84,0:47:05.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nice. Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.80,0:47:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameraman: Are you giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.66,0:47:10.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.11,0:47:16.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a thanks to the cameraman for taking a picture of the two on Kachidoki bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.03,0:47:18.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this one it is clear where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.01,0:47:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.95,0:47:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.16,0:47:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They've grown so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.02,0:47:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At that age I thought the two would fight. But they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.95,0:47:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a nice relationship. \NI got so nervous when they found the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.96,0:47:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they are kids they directly point it out.\N If it was an adult they would behave since it's for TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lie about measuring electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.74,0:47:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cameraman just ignored them. \NCan't believe such a simple trick worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.39,0:47:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply crossing a bridge can be a huge adventure for a child. Do any of you have experience with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.03,0:48:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My fathers parents live in Miyagi so in elementary school I would go there every summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.38,0:48:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go on adventure in the mountains by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.64,0:48:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would tell me to only go exactly this far in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.90,0:48:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year I would go further across the boundary.\NThat's what it made me think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.70,0:48:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Stand By Me taking place in Miyagi prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.21,0:48:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next errand, a girl who like her father is a bit ditzy and forgetful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.18,0:48:37.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Seto Inland Sea is a town called Niochou.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.89,0:48:38.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.87,0:48:42.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here they still make salt in the traditional way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.53,0:48:47.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Especially the fairytale-like scenery of Chichibuga seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.14,0:48:44.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.13,0:48:50.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This place is currently very popular among young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.69,0:48:55.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's very popular for snapping Instagram photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.25,0:48:55.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.27,0:48:57.03,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.02,0:49:01.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At that place a father and daughter are taking pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.89,0:49:02.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,Her posture is like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.32,0:49:08.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually, her father is a pro cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.85,0:49:09.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.56,0:49:16.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is An who will go on an errand. She is 4 years and 1 month old and has a younger brother who is 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.62,0:49:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her father is bringing her up in his own home town.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.74,0:49:23.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This old part of town remains like a time capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.08,0:49:27.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They purchased an old Japanese home 3 years ago and turned it into an office.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.84,0:49:31.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They hope to establish a business of long standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.59,0:49:36.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This neighborhood used to be sprawling as a shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.59,0:49:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(162.909,619.818)}1958
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.14,0:49:41.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While the times have changed what remains the same is the shrine that stands strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.27,0:49:45.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It goes back to the Edo period and has continued throughout Meiji until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.20,0:49:50.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a pamphlet with pictures the father has taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.43,0:49:55.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The handmade bread of the old baker lady or a diner. It's full of great information.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.97,0:50:00.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is now gathering information for a new edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.65,0:50:05.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's the type who becomes oblivious of their surroundings when focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.37,0:50:07.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He also forgets a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.64,0:50:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An watches her father and his hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.37,0:50:13.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the gets home that day she immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.86,0:50:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.74,0:50:17.17,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Again with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.16,0:50:18.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.23,0:50:19.99,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,He forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.98,0:50:21.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's his water bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.15,0:50:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.80,0:50:25.85,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Father is such a forgetful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.30,0:50:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.29,0:50:29.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.85,0:50:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone. It's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.68,0:50:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.58,0:50:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.22,0:50:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my water bottle. \NAn, can't you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.63,0:50:43.40,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.39,0:50:45.32,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.39,0:50:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.69,0:50:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I also need a cream puff for work reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.46,0:50:55.93,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will purchase a cream puff for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.27,0:50:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.62,0:51:01.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's located next to the town shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.56,0:51:05.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's mainly a place for traditional Japanese confectionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.44,0:51:11.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The third generation owner has started selling cream puffs with a luxury sugar called Sanuki sanbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.22,0:51:13.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a very popular item.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.32,0:51:14.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.00,0:51:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Also at Nori's place buy a trash bag \Nsince I have to clean up around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.26,0:51:21.24,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.26,0:51:23.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Along with her small good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.81,0:51:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She first has to walk 20 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.03,0:51:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the soy sauce makers house.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.81,0:51:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In old times they used to make soy sauce here but now they just sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.54,0:51:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They also sell trash bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.89,0:51:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The cream puffs are sold next to the shrine. \NAll in all 450 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.51,0:51:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a neighorhood errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.59,0:51:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.78,0:51:50.00,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.64,0:51:57.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In her hands is her dads free pamphlet along with an empty box to put purchased items in.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.23,0:51:58.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,Hard to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.01,0:52:00.06,Studio,,0,0,0,,Instead of a shopping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.08,0:52:07.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is wondering if she will \Nbe fine since An takes after her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.29,0:52:09.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's looking at the pahmplet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.61,0:52:13.22,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs for dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.49,0:52:14.79,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.78,0:52:19.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. But before that she has to purchase the trash bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.42,0:52:22.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, she just passed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.51,0:52:25.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will be late if I don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.62,0:52:27.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For the cream puffs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.55,0:52:29.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait. Why did she turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.81,0:52:33.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A building has popped up on this otherwise plain parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.36,0:52:39.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a brand new specialty show for handmade cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.85,0:52:42.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Two cream puffs, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.59,0:52:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.73,0:52:49.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They usually make round birthday cakes upon request.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.25,0:52:51.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They don't even have a display counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.69,0:52:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Two cream puffs? One?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.50,0:52:55.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They also make cream puffs here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.84,0:52:59.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will take her order since she's come all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.90,0:53:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take a little while. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.67,0:53:06.12,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.11,0:53:08.24,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.11,0:53:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.23,0:53:10.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has made an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.67,0:53:15.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she wasn't asked to purchase cream puffs from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.69,0:53:20.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After ordering the cream puffs she suddenly remembers to trash bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.98,0:53:25.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He even mentioned the day before \Nthat he intends to clean up his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.17,0:53:30.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop owners are way back in the home part of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.53,0:53:34.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can she say "trash bags, please" in a loud voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.81,0:53:38.28,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cardboard box, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.80,0:53:40.83,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cardboard box, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.84,0:53:43.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wasn't asked to get a cardboard box at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.34,0:53:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.76,0:53:45.79,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,A cardboard box.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.78,0:53:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A cardboard box? Is that what you are looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.23,0:53:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not vinegar? Did they really ask you to get a cardboard box?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.07,0:53:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? A cardboard box.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.95,0:53:59.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are lots of cardboard boxes but...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.99,0:54:02.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If it's a cardboard box how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.03,0:54:06.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She found an empty box that had \Nsoy sauce in it. She will give it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.19,0:54:09.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can you take it? \N Are you doing an errand for your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.87,0:54:11.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.32,0:54:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Smart kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.43,0:54:13.94,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go to my dad's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.93,0:54:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are heading there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.39,0:54:16.59,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.58,0:54:19.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's no trash can in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.93,0:54:24.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For this old district this might be a better way to throw things out in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.64,0:54:31.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's tottering along. \NBut it's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.58,0:54:41.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She put it down? Is she taking a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.67,0:54:45.44,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Right, left. All clear, I can continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.94,0:54:46.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.81,0:54:49.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her father has taught her how to be safe in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:52.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Head straight through the crossroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.23,0:54:54.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's carrying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.63,0:54:57.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, she turned left?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.10,0:54:59.18,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Heading for dads job.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.17,0:55:02.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The staff who were on the right route have to catch up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.38,0:55:06.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she didn't head for the right shop this way is actually faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.31,0:55:08.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are so many narrow streets around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.91,0:55:13.13,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.12,0:55:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.11,0:55:17.89,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,They will be making the cream puffs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.88,0:55:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Making them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.04,0:55:19.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.67,0:55:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I use this as a trash bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:24.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep. Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.62,0:55:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.63,0:55:27.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.08,0:55:29.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I can use this. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.21,0:55:31.25,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,And I brought your water bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.24,0:55:33.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing her father forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.44,0:55:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. You did it all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.79,0:55:37.59,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.58,0:55:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But An...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.46,0:55:43.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be the case that they haven't made cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.16,0:55:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see this, An?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.94,0:55:45.84,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.83,0:55:47.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A picture of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.39,0:55:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.39,0:55:49.75,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go and purchase cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.49,0:55:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.53,0:55:58.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has seen the front of the building this time. \NI wonder if she will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.65,0:56:01.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's looking at the pamphlet and comparing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.13,0:56:04.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Japanese confectionary shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.06,0:56:06.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop is here if she turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.70,0:56:10.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However she went straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.96,0:56:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Made to run. \N - The adults are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.46,0:56:16.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rather than shooting they are running more.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.69,0:56:17.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,So fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.20,0:56:19.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They must also be heading for that famous shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.65,0:56:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.20,0:56:23.76,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs. Cream puffs. Cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.75,0:56:25.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's been out for less than 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.46,0:56:31.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"She's already back" the shop owner must be wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.67,0:56:43.33,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.32,0:56:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't baked yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.12,0:56:48.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.40,0:56:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take a bit longer. Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.53,0:56:53.91,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.90,0:56:57.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Despite having seen the picture of the correct shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.31,0:57:01.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She didn't notice that this is a different shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.84,0:57:01.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,She runs so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.08,0:57:03.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's going back to her fathers place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.51,0:57:06.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the staff is trying to reach the office first.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.91,0:57:08.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,How rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.92,0:57:10.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She went straight ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.63,0:57:12.98,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Better visit the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.63,0:57:12.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,The shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.97,0:57:16.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone is competing against An.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.35,0:57:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So many are coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.85,0:57:19.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.85,0:57:21.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.55,0:57:28.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When out for walks with her mother she always visits this shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.09,0:57:32.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These rocks are called Shimeishi and can be found in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.19,0:57:35.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've been here since over 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.48,0:57:40.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Jingle jangle, she's rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.00,0:57:42.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How many yen will she put out?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.44,0:57:44.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's not putting anything in?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.33,0:57:46.23,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.79,0:57:48.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,A shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.82,0:57:49.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's already leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.80,0:57:52.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She didn't even make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.33,0:57:57.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameramen have no clue anymore. \N They are being made to follow her whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.58,0:58:04.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An is giving the fight of her life. \NBut what she intends to do is hard to decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.38,0:58:04.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.01,0:58:05.72,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,They are still making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.71,0:58:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They are still making them? \N What did the old guy say?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.01,0:58:12.93,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What? It was an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.92,0:58:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Old woman? And she's making them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.18,0:58:17.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, was there ever a woman running that shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.93,0:58:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Which shop did you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.76,0:58:21.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.84,0:58:27.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did you go to the wrong shop? \NThe shop is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.47,0:58:29.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go towards the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.29,0:58:36.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are many narrow streets here but if she goes this way it will be easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.10,0:58:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.01,0:58:41.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's easier to spot from this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.32,0:58:42.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.33,0:58:43.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,Why why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.14,0:58:45.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.91,0:58:46.34,Studio,,0,0,0,,Her conviction is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.54,0:58:50.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's inherited this from her dad that she refuses to bow down from her opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.19,0:58:52.20,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What color coin should I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.19,0:58:53.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.20,0:58:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The brown coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.44,0:58:57.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She didn't know the kind of money to put in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.23,0:58:59.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.08,0:58:59.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.62,0:59:02.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. The shrine is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sponsor announcement]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.40,0:59:25.93,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I wish my mother will not be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:28.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother said she had a sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.72,0:59:32.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rather than the cream puffs \Nthe most important thing is mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.25,0:59:34.39,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,, Ah, it was over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.38,0:59:35.78,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.77,0:59:38.68,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs. Cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.67,0:59:41.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop is just outside of the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.84,0:59:44.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why is she going to the side?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.06,0:59:47.21,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.20,0:59:49.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From all the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.07,0:59:52.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She taking a small break.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.14,0:59:55.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's just taking the blouse off.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.16,0:59:57.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's confirming that she didn't forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.78,0:59:59.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.35,1:00:01.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She should see the shop just up the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.05,1:00:04.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman has gone in first.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.00,1:00:07.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Look behind you. Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.72,1:00:09.71,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.12,1:00:14.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She went back even though it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.17,1:00:16.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why can't she spot it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.64,1:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, An?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.24,1:00:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you purchase it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.46,1:00:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Great that you came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.96,1:00:25.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She didn't mention the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.56,1:00:27.24,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.56,1:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not spot it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.23,1:00:28.76,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.23,1:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.75,1:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An, perhaps you didn't see the picture. \N The front looks like this. The sign has green and red letters.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.52,1:00:38.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to look at this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.83,1:00:44.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An was looking at the cream puff picture. \N She wasn't looking at the facade.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.68,1:00:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go. This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.42,1:00:51.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Around the corner here. Take care and thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.64,1:00:54.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the 4th trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.38,1:00:58.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time she is looking at the shop facade.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.97,1:01:01.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can she find it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.07,1:01:05.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's right there. The green and red letters on the sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.28,1:01:09.96,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.95,1:01:11.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.40,1:01:16.85,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Right, left. All clear, I can continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.80,1:01:17.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.85,1:01:22.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's doing it properly. \N But she's also hurrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.56,1:01:27.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was asked to purchase two.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.14,1:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.89,1:01:32.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One cream puff two of those.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.80,1:01:34.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.99,1:01:39.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has them. These are those made with wasanbon sugar.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.29,1:01:44.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One is 175 yen. She put out a 1000 bill so now her purse will jangle even more.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.88,1:01:48.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She became even richer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.49,1:01:50.33,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.49,1:01:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the way back?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.36,1:01:52.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.68,1:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.28,1:01:55.17,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1083.636,327.454)\fs55\frz12.77}Phew.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.38,1:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.54,1:01:57.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a cookie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.51,1:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.77,1:02:00.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She received a reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.61,1:02:04.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You're welcome. Take care on your way back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.61,1:02:03.69,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.27,1:02:05.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After saying her thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.94,1:02:09.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Right, left. All clear, I can continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.29,1:02:10.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Being safe in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.64,1:02:12.06,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.05,1:02:14.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can finally return.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.68,1:02:16.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will give it to dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.40,1:02:17.88,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.06,1:02:20.28,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.06,1:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to buy it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.27,1:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.78,1:02:24.20,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I found it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.19,1:02:25.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.92,1:02:29.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's take some pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.36,1:02:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.84,1:02:34.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's properly assisting with the reflector board.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.88,1:02:38.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad looks cool as he is focused on taking the pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.67,1:02:39.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.92,1:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.38,1:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.03,1:02:49.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's why she likes photoshoots of food.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.69,1:02:52.77,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.76,1:02:57.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, she forgot. She ordered cream puffs at this shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.18,1:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dad doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.76,1:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.76,1:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He only knew about the shop over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.67,1:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He really made her walk around.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.67,1:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a proper reason to get those.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.05,1:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.64,1:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you were crying a bit during the conundrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.18,1:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.18,1:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was touched when she properly asked \Nfor her mothers good health.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.92,1:03:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very touching.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.27,1:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes me curious about the cream puffs she ordered.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.05,1:03:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder until how late the old lady waited for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.61,1:03:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016.727,628.546)\fs30}On the way back from the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.67,1:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As a gift for her mother that had a sore throat \N they apparently collected it on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.44,1:03:39.72,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.93,1:03:43.02,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,The bus will be here in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.01,1:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These brothers will ride a bus to complete their errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.29,1:03:49.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's so small.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.66,1:03:56.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 4 year and 3 months old brother and his little brother \Nat 2 years and 4 months who keeps asking if it's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.92,1:03:54.04,GreenFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,326)}Shuya
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.96,1:03:54.04,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(197.818,333.273)}Kanaya
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.03,1:04:04.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who planned this errand and let his little brother join is their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.46,1:04:01.73,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's standing there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.46,1:04:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As their mother I am confident that they can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.58,1:04:12.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Some strong words. \NShe has a special memory associated with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.86,1:04:20.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The city of Ikeda in Tokushima prefecture where the dad who loves mountains was brought up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.15,1:04:25.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad purchased a house with a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.61,1:04:27.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The wall is full of family pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.98,1:04:32.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When the kids were smaller or that time they visited Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.20,1:04:37.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the four years of their marriage the wall has already filled up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.63,1:04:42.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the dad is no longer with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.39,1:04:45.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He died 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.10,1:04:51.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He left for his lumberjack job as usual on that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.42,1:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1093.818,618.364)\fs30}Location of the accident
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.77,1:04:55.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But a tree suddenly fell on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.47,1:05:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When papa died I cried so much. \NThe two of us did. Every evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.81,1:05:15.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was just after the little brother was born. The one who was always by his mothers side was the 2 year old brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.20,1:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It hit me like a switch. I don't remember when. \NSuddenly I just decided not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.45,1:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry anymore. Won't cry \Nin front of the kids anymore. Not again.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.92,1:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that day I decided that while there are dads and mothers I need to fulfill both of those roles.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.68,1:05:40.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother behaves properly after having watched his mother from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.73,1:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When the little brother becomes unmanageable the one to take the reins is the big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.02,1:05:52.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's like he has taken the responsibility of his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.76,1:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I rely on the big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.87,1:06:02.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother loves to make his mother happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.96,1:06:08.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father loved tulips. \N Just as he loved nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.40,1:06:12.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So for the errand they've decided to get some flowers for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.70,1:06:16.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kanaya at 2 years and four months still doesn't talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.48,1:06:20.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he's fine with his brother on his side.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.55,1:06:22.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He depends on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.20,1:06:24.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus which is running late finally came.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.85,1:06:26.05,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,It came.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.26,1:06:29.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Stop, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.00,1:06:30.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed the brothers hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.84,1:06:31.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.95,1:06:38.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What a relief. This bus comes once every 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.71,1:06:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They rode it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.37,1:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They rode it. It's hard to see because of the tinted windows.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.76,1:06:47.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The windows on the bus are tinted.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.53,1:06:53.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman rehearsed this shot with the bus that passed 2 hours earlier and has waited since then.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.10,1:06:57.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eh? With this type of windows we can't look inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.92,1:06:57.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.68,1:06:59.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.80,1:07:05.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Big brother looks serious. \N And with his bright red cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.94,1:07:08.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about the youngest of them?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.34,1:07:15.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Getting sleepy from the ride but he has nothing to worry about. Since his brother is by his side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.27,1:07:20.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Protect him, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.55,1:07:20.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.46,1:07:23.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.43,1:07:30.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus has arrived at the terminal. \NThis is also where they should catch it on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.06,1:07:32.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:39.62,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,We are getting off, Kanaya. You can't sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.61,1:07:45.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've received the bus fare separately. \NOh no, this is for the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.42,1:07:47.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no, he took out the 1000 yen bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.85,1:07:50.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now the purse is full of spare change.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.97,1:07:55.27,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Let's walk to the flower shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.26,1:07:58.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, they have to walk to the flower shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.69,1:08:03.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The road is straight forward. \NThey always come by car here with their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.56,1:08:07.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They might not notice when going by car\N but the street is on a slope.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.15,1:08:10.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which they have to ascend on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.98,1:08:16.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore it takes about 2 hours to go there and back. \NThere's no time to roam around.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.78,1:08:16.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,Better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.03,1:08:20.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have to walk in line \N since the pavement is narrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.86,1:08:23.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's properly following his big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.46,1:08:27.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kanaya doesn't speak but he's good on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.85,1:08:29.00,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.99,1:08:29.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hole?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.39,1:08:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are taught to walk in the line\N where the holes are by their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.51,1:08:38.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His brother is checking if Kanaya is walking properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.06,1:08:44.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the check they can continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.80,1:08:44.23,Studio,,0,0,0,,Pushed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.67,1:08:55.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But their speeds are completely different. \N Little brother who can't speak a word wants to call out "wait".
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.32,1:08:58.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.00,1:09:03.64,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,You've become capable of saying "brobro", Kanaya?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.51,1:09:09.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first words and they were "brobro".
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.99,1:09:11.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A rapid development on this errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.47,1:09:17.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When you follow your brother with all your might you grow strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.23,1:09:19.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.32,1:09:20.68,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hand hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.67,1:09:22.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He even said "hands".
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.02,1:09:26.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even at home there are times \Nwhen he doesn't want to hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.19,1:09:30.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But today is an errand and his brother is his new father-figure.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.83,1:09:33.03,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.02,1:09:35.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They can see the flower shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.01,1:09:42.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their father would often stop by \N to purchase flowers for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.06,1:09:46.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He would get the flowers of the season every week.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.35,1:09:52.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their father who worked in the mountain-side especially prefered bigleaf hydrangea.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.14,1:09:56.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even their mother comes here every week.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.90,1:09:57.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop owner is an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.88,1:10:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.39,1:10:01.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where's mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.64,1:10:03.85,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,She's at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.84,1:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you and your brother come alone?\N What a smart kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.28,1:10:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come here to buy?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.30,1:10:11.22,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.21,1:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.28,1:10:16.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone remembers that his dad used to come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.53,1:10:21.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Carnations, lillies and sunflowers.\NThey have all kinds of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.43,1:10:25.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The shop owner is making them a bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.13,1:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any color you would like to add?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.52,1:10:28.36,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Red.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.35,1:10:30.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Red, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.28,1:10:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.08,1:10:35.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I see. Adding red has made is livelier.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.26,1:10:38.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother has a nice taste.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.09,1:10:41.96,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Please add a pink ribbon for mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.95,1:10:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For mom, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.47,1:10:47.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's what his father used to do too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.21,1:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.83,1:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give this to your mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.83,1:10:52.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He decided without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.12,1:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will wrap it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.87,1:10:56.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yellow is his little brothers favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.18,1:10:57.74,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.73,1:10:59.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.86,1:11:03.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since they are a present.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.36,1:11:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The ones he chose were alstroemeria. \NAlso called Lily of the Incas.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.67,1:11:12.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man is even giving him a card to write on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.09,1:11:14.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can even write?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.78,1:11:15.27,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He can write?\N - That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.44,1:11:17.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is he writing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.38,1:11:17.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,- What is this? \N- No clue.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.36,1:11:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.05,1:11:21.06,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.62,1:11:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can write it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.47,1:11:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It said thank you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.15,1:11:28.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The man wrote thanks to the mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.32,1:11:29.41,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.40,1:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Also to your dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.78,1:11:33.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And thanks to his little brother too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.50,1:11:35.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hand it over both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.24,1:11:37.43,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.57,1:11:37.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.09,708.546)}you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.42,1:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.61,1:11:40.58,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.57,1:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.17,1:11:48.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's only an hour left before the bus departs. \NAnd they have to purchase some things first.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.52,1:11:54.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The supermarket is next to the bus terminal. \NWhat they are getting is coffee and udon noodles.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.92,1:11:57.01,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.00,1:11:58.55,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.54,1:12:01.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They've started going up the hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.15,1:12:03.16,Studio,,0,0,0,,Even if he is asked to hurry...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.11,1:12:06.18,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.17,1:12:10.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They haven't noticed when going by car \Nbut it's pretty steep.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.86,1:12:12.50,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.49,1:12:15.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This won't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.37,1:12:14.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.04,1:12:17.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They won't make it at this pace.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.74,1:12:20.83,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.82,1:12:23.43,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Give it all you got.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.42,1:12:30.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you shout for this 2 year old who just spoke his first words he doesn't know what "hurry" means.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.59,1:12:33.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he is properly walking above the holes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.24,1:12:34.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.87,1:12:35.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,Adhering to the rule
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.04,1:12:37.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This way he won't walk into the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.23,1:12:41.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His brother has decided to leave him behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.11,1:12:41.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.84,1:12:44.71,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.70,1:12:51.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They won't make it at this pace. \NHe has decided to go shopping ahead of his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.86,1:12:55.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Over the holes. Over the holes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.61,1:12:57.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The supermarket is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.72,1:12:59.88,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.87,1:13:02.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The road is flat here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.23,1:13:04.44,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,The supermarket is right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.43,1:13:07.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a large-sized supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.92,1:13:10.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this moment how is Kanaya doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.73,1:13:17.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With two traffic lights ahead of him if he walks \Nabove the holes he will reach up with his brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.30,1:13:15.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,Move forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.80,1:13:24.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But there's only 30 minutes before the bus leaves.\NWill they make it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.72,1:13:20.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.32,1:13:26.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The big brother has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.17,1:13:28.18,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I would like some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.17,1:13:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrated coffee?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.80,1:13:33.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found the coffee at the beverage aisle.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.95,1:13:35.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is your mother looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.95,1:13:38.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Only for dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.95,1:13:38.70,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Only for dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.69,1:13:40.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Smokes and coffee reminds them of dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.22,1:13:47.05,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,And there must also be some udon here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.04,1:13:50.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He remembers well always getting these with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.36,1:13:52.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His little brother loves udon.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.12,1:13:57.32,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.31,1:14:00.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it really that heavy?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.49,1:14:01.78,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.76,1:14:04.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found all he needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.73,1:14:07.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Kanaya is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.23,1:14:12.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was told to walk on the bumpy lines after the holes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.52,1:14:12.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.43,1:14:14.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The supermarket is within sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.12,1:14:14.00,Studio,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.60,1:14:14.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.70,1:14:16.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where's brobro?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.13,1:14:19.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Brobro is still in the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.80,1:14:22.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Putting all the items in the backpack.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.89,1:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.27,1:14:27.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time will run out if you don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.80,1:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Better hurry. \N- Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.12,1:14:34.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's 10 minutes to and people have started gathering.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.22,1:14:36.46,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Where's Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.58,1:14:42.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He believes Kanaya has kept walking far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.38,1:14:44.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.75,1:14:46.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.36,1:14:48.47,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.46,1:14:50.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.00,1:14:52.29,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,He's calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.28,1:14:55.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.83,1:14:54.79,Studio,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.16,1:14:57.59,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.58,1:14:58.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.11,1:15:02.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Found him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.41,1:15:06.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like his brother believed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.66,1:15:06.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.39,1:15:08.43,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.42,1:15:11.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't it nice that he can say brobro now.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.39,1:15:15.91,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I got coffee and udon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.46,1:15:15.91,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's talking normally to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.90,1:15:17.74,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Udon and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.43,1:15:25.28,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Come to the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.94,1:15:28.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The little brother is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.70,1:15:34.89,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Kanaya, do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.88,1:15:36.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.76,1:15:41.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Finally leaving the bumpy lines they get together for an emotional meet up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.28,1:15:42.70,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.89,1:15:46.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He really did his best not to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.51,1:15:46.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.76,1:15:49.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What? Aren't we going to hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.81,1:15:51.56,Studio,,0,0,0,,He clearly put out his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.83,1:15:56.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he made it this far by himself he wants his brother to finish on his own. Like a father.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.65,1:16:01.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They made it just in time with 5 minutes to spare.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.69,1:16:01.85,Studio,,0,0,0,,They gave it their all.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.19,1:16:15.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bus home doesn't have tinted windows. \NWith this we should be able to see the two from outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.10,1:16:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1009.454,605.273)\fs28}Original Song: \N藤田麻衣子 - 素敵なことがあなたを待っている
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.76,1:16:23.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Back to the cameraman who waited for over 2 hours\Nhe put a lot of care into getting a glimpse of the two.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.82,1:16:23.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do you best.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.58,1:16:27.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Where are they? Huh, they aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.46,1:16:33.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Can't see them cause they are asleep. \N Even big brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.18,1:16:36.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From all the stress surrounding the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.79,1:16:45.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end we didn't get a single glimpse of them going either of the directions.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.46,1:16:51.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the bus stop after crossing the river. \NIf they don't wake up they will go all the way to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.93,1:16:57.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Their mother is waiting at the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.48,1:17:01.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's wondering if they made it to the bus.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.51,1:17:06.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.54,1:17:06.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,Sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.00,1:17:09.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.03,1:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are there any kids on board?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.95,1:17:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I take a look? \N - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.94,1:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Must be asleep. \N- I bet they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.85,1:17:29.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.18,1:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please wait a little bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.61,1:17:36.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kanaya who kept walking above the holes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.81,1:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuuya.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.14,1:17:40.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shuuya who has become brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.38,1:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.05,1:17:42.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,He gave it all he had.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.48,1:17:44.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,He looks so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.92,1:17:48.05,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you come all the way to get us?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.04,1:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly 280 yen. Thank you for taking care of us. Ah, and I'm sorry it dragged out.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.02,1:17:56.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She also thanks the other riders.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.50,1:18:03.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hold up. It wasn't just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.84,1:18:07.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I really did go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.14,1:18:10.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's fine. He even brought proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.22,1:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Are these flowers for dad?\NAnd are these for mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.14,1:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you write here?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.23,1:18:23.37,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,Just to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.36,1:18:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.80,1:18:32.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I saw it. Also for dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.80,1:18:32.79,WhiteGreenBorder,,0,0,0,,I wrote it to you, mom. And also for dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.78,1:18:37.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dad, they've become able to purchase flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.25,1:18:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat udon with broth.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.16,1:18:42.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her laughter has returned to her voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.33,1:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.70,1:18:49.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Kanaya has started speaking. He said "brobro".
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.05,1:18:53.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As usual next to their father you find flowers and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.00,1:18:58.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father, let's depend on big brother to bring you flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.50,1:19:06.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Father lives on inside both of Shuuya and Kanaya.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.37,1:19:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- What a perfect errand. \N- That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.19,1:19:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At the beginning when the mother was standing strong I thought what a hard mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.33,1:19:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.26,1:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought what a hard-disciplining mother\Nbut then it turned out that she was kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.86,1:19:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried a lot. Especially considering the younger is 2 years old and staying by his brothers side.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.98,1:19:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that boys have a strong feeling towards wanting to protect their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.08,1:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as wanting to be helpful to their mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.78,1:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And especially when there is a younger brother in play the older becomes aware of the role the play.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.60,1:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.65,1:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a big brother here who was crying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.54,1:20:14.13,WhiteRedBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(533.818,586.364)}Wailing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.12,1:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. I just couldn't keep it in. \N - I kept hearing "uuh uuh" next to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.03,1:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Shuuya was almost like watching myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.92,1:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.93,1:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.95,1:20:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the first time I've been able to say it. Brobro.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.11,1:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's your first time saying it? I see. \N- Brobro. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.35,1:20:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next will be our youngest to go on an errand for this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.08,1:20:43.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A small town called Nishiiya in the mountains of Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.56,1:20:47.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A 2 year old and 2 months old will go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.94,1:20:56.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you go there you will notice that hardly any cars drive on the road. It's a very quiet place.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.11,1:20:58.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the only shop here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.36,1:21:05.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Food, alcohol, soy sauce, tissues and even emergency drugs are available here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.28,1:21:07.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The towns convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.01,1:21:10.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's been in operation for 87 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.44,1:21:18.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This shop hasn't changed and people love it for it. \NThe ones running it are the Kitas.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.59,1:21:25.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since this place is so safe and our kid is capable her mother has asked us to film the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.28,1:21:30.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Say "welcome".
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.59,1:21:34.58,Studio,,0,0,0,,- No way. \N - This kid? \N - She's so small.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.56,1:21:36.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just a toddler?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.87,1:21:36.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,Can this kid do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.43,1:21:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread please.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.05,1:21:41.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We don't meet the children until the day of shooting.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.79,1:21:43.14,VioletFill,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.636,238.727)}Yumemi
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.44,1:21:45.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our program aims not to prefer any children over others.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.37,1:21:48.66,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Today we have Anpan bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.65,1:21:50.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.48,1:21:53.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it really this kid? \NNot an older sister or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.89,1:21:55.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We called out the mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.50,1:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that kid Yumemi?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.28,1:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it Yume? \N - It's Yume.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.65,1:22:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't she too small? \N- She's small?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.08,1:22:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can she go on an errand? \N- An errand? Yeah, she's in a good mood today.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.23,1:22:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mood? Are you confident? \N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.04,1:22:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told her to go to the swings she ran towards it alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.07,1:22:29.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So it's really this kid. Since the 16 staffers came all the way from Tokyo let's just see how it plays out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.44,1:22:31.94,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Poi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.93,1:22:33.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.32,1:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So many toys. The bag is going to be full.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.27,1:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this bag might not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.27,1:22:40.61,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Can it all fit in?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.94,1:22:41.87,Studio,,0,0,0,,She can conversate.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.60,1:22:43.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She understands quantities.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.00,1:22:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it won't. Do we have another bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.00,1:22:48.11,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It won't be able to close.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.10,1:22:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look if we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.58,1:22:55.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will she be able to spot the right item.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.47,1:22:57.88,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,There ain't one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.03,1:22:58.67,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ain't one?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.17,1:23:01.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've probably run out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.39,1:23:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.54,1:23:06.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if asked such a question. \NShe's holding the remote to the AC.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.63,1:23:09.36,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.63,1:23:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.35,1:23:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a request to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.87,1:23:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've run out of bags.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.87,1:23:17.21,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.20,1:23:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm waiting for the electrician and can't leave home. Wonder who can purchase them instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.64,1:23:26.95,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yume will go buy them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.94,1:23:30.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.94,1:23:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you buy them? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.44,1:23:32.98,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.44,1:23:32.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's at the old man Kita's place.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.97,1:23:37.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pass the school, go up the hill and then buy it. \NAre you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.05,1:23:37.93,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.92,1:23:41.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.92,1:23:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A bag? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.29,1:23:43.16,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.29,1:23:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really make this request?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.15,1:23:44.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.22,1:23:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another request.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.13,1:23:48.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Another request?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.91,1:23:50.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I want this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.22,1:23:51.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A toy egg.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.84,1:23:54.10,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's an egg.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.84,1:23:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.09,1:23:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I would also like eggs for todays lunch since we've run out. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.56,1:24:01.07,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.06,1:24:04.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the usual route to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.67,1:24:09.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was asked to get bags and eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.40,1:24:11.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've left a camera on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.42,1:24:13.89,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mom, eggs... wait what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.88,1:24:15.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Immediately spotted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.04,1:24:16.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.24,1:24:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was left by a construction worker.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.24,1:24:19.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.45,1:24:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.67,1:24:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, departing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.67,1:24:23.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Departure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.29,1:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to sit on each step to go down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.57,1:24:30.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Each step requires this much effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.47,1:24:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.73,1:24:34.69,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Heading off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.01,1:24:39.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mother is a former Japanese teacher. \NA real pro in education.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.20,1:24:44.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A besides bringing up a kid she's already brought up two older sisters.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.66,1:24:52.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And she has taught Yumemi that she can accomplish anything. She can even talk really well.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.33,1:24:58.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, she stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.22,1:25:02.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sticking to the wall and checking out her surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.48,1:25:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she go back now?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.80,1:25:06.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She started moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.86,1:25:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's going out after all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.16,1:25:13.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's cautious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.68,1:25:17.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yumemi is careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.00,1:25:24.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has started spinning.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.26,1:25:26.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Spinning one round.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.38,1:25:30.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then another.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.02,1:25:34.13,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.12,1:25:38.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mama? Will she go back home?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.78,1:25:36.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.37,1:25:44.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.95,1:25:58.38,Studio,,0,0,0,, Where to?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.82,1:26:02.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She started climbing the hill. \NThis road leads to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.51,1:26:08.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's putting all her power \Ninto climbing the 13 degree slope.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.00,1:26:09.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.13,1:26:12.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's her mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.37,1:26:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.37,1:26:14.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's watching her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.64,1:26:17.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is she crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.95,1:26:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.13,1:26:25.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do your best. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.13,1:26:25.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one crying is the mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.16,1:26:26.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yumemi isn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.86,1:26:30.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.81,1:26:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One two. One two.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.33,1:26:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One two.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.70,1:26:39.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She suddenly turned her back and started picking her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.81,1:26:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.81,1:26:41.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Departure.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.57,1:26:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mom isn't there to stop her from picking her nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.16,1:26:51.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's really going for it. \NWe might've underestimated her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.80,1:26:54.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Still going up the hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.05,1:27:01.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She stopped again. \NLooking back at her home.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.51,1:27:08.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's making a grimace. \NIs she going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.43,1:27:13.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her seeking pose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.43,1:27:13.50,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Where is mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.49,1:27:17.83,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.49,1:27:17.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her shouting out pose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.70,1:27:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.75,1:27:22.40,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.39,1:27:26.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All that searching and shouting out but mama isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.17,1:27:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She keeps searching.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.36,1:27:33.51,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What should I do. Mama...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.36,1:27:33.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is her thinking pose.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.54,1:27:35.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.42,1:27:40.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's really going for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.17,1:27:43.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.08,1:27:49.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yumemi has reached the top of the hill\N and is heading for the shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.44,1:27:55.36,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594.909,557.273)}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.34,1:27:57.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's greeting our traffic patrol.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.41,1:28:02.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's straight ahead. The shop's \Nred banner is visible from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.82,1:28:05.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,I can see it too.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.35,1:28:10.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows to walk on the edge of the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.87,1:28:18.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's walking on the stone lids \Nlike her mother taught her
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.75,1:28:20.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.37,1:28:25.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh, the cameraman was in the way. \NWe are sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.48,1:28:29.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did she fall?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.64,1:28:37.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No, she's just sitting. This is the usual spot she has a break when she's out walking with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.95,1:28:40.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is it someone she knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.87,1:28:43.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old lady of the health clinic.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.03,1:28:50.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She greets them every time they go for a walk. \NAnd she's even bringing candy?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.47,1:28:52.76,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.47,1:28:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.75,1:28:54.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She knows to properly say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.46,1:28:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.76,1:29:00.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her cherished Madeleine cakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.38,1:29:00.01,Studio,,0,0,0,,This is the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.49,1:29:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.76,1:29:04.61,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.76,1:29:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.60,1:29:11.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not only candy but watching and protecting from afar that's the love that goes around in this town.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.68,1:29:09.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.26,1:29:14.19,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will keep walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.47,1:29:20.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After a short rest and she's ready to walk again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.20,1:29:25.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's a Madelaine crumb left on her cheeck.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.69,1:29:27.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.87,1:29:36.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She was asked to get bags and eggs. \NComing from outside it's quite dark inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.48,1:29:39.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's intimidated by going in.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.86,1:29:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come by yourself? How clever you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.29,1:29:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.46,1:29:51.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eggs? How many?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.73,1:29:54.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two? Two eggs?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.16,1:29:57.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No way she can carry two containers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.45,1:29:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.41,1:30:02.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But the old lady took out two eggs and placed them in a bag for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.36,1:30:02.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,How kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.59,1:30:05.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Cause that's how they were sold in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.53,1:30:10.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They will never be able to sell this container.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.02,1:30:12.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 83 year old husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.75,1:30:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.01,1:30:16.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the conversation with this tiny customer.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.73,1:30:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come alone? How clever you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.22,1:30:23.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's being praised.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.55,1:30:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting eggs?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.89,1:30:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She does?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.89,1:30:30.75,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama loves them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.59,1:30:37.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And she was able to come by herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.59,1:30:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's become more conversational since last.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.71,1:30:41.11,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.71,1:30:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a frog.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.85,1:30:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.50,1:30:45.42,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.41,1:30:53.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 years and 2 months and an 83 year old. \NTheir conversation tempo oddly suit each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.01,1:30:58.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(190,119.818)}She's so excited.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.21,1:31:00.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yumemi, you still haven't finished the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.93,1:31:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumemi, are you only getting eggs?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.59,1:31:08.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's searching for the forgotten thing in her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.91,1:31:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did mama ask you to buy?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.32,1:31:13.49,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,And bags too.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.48,1:31:15.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.16,1:31:22.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When she's asked she will remember. \NThe old lady brings out the bags for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.91,1:31:25.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She also knows that she needs to pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.89,1:31:26.81,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.80,1:31:30.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Putting out 500 yen and getting her money back. She did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.97,1:31:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Praiseworthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.43,1:31:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.52,1:31:38.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.52,1:31:38.59,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.58,1:31:41.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.59,1:31:45.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To avoid the eggs from cracking he puts them in her purse.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.69,1:31:47.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.69,1:31:48.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Say your goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.24,1:31:51.60,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,{\fs28}Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.24,1:31:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.85,1:31:54.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She won't say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.10,1:31:57.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.10,1:31:57.50,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.88,1:31:58.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200.182,118.364)}Doesn't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.49,1:32:01.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While they say goodbye the old man slowly moves away.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.90,1:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.73,1:32:09.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yumemi finds it hard to go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.04,1:32:11.61,Studio,,0,0,0,,-What a weird scene. \N\N- Gramps be careful of things behind you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.72,1:32:15.80,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.79,1:32:20.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The old man is now much further away.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.10,1:32:22.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.091,103.818)}This is quite moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.15,1:32:27.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.20,1:32:30.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with that the old man...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.31,1:32:33.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,disappears from view.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.03,1:32:34.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Their bond is so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.92,1:32:38.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright Yumemi, that was the goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.88,1:32:43.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After having so much fun she remembers her mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.58,1:32:45.70,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.55,1:32:46.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.34,1:32:51.45,Studio,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.59,1:32:58.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's taking a secret shortcut through the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.64,1:33:00.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.364,115.455)}She knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.95,1:33:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.52,1:33:06.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can see her home from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.66,1:33:10.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother can see someone in pink clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.81,1:33:13.54,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yu.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.53,1:33:15.25,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Oh, mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.24,1:33:16.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.40,1:33:20.09,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home. I brought the bags.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.08,1:33:24.29,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.00,1:33:32.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her mother thinks she forgot all about the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.11,1:33:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.52,1:33:40.43,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.42,1:33:42.41,Studio,,0,0,0,,Both the kid and the mom are.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.40,1:33:46.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One by one she climbs the stairs with all her might.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.74,1:33:49.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The goal is her mothers arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.28,1:33:53.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you for getting it for me. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.83,1:33:59.83,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.83,1:33:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.82,1:34:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the bags for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.48,1:34:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you forgot the eggs?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.14,1:34:05.86,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.89,1:34:07.27,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I have them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.26,1:34:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You do? Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.95,1:34:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.95,1:34:12.31,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.30,1:34:14.52,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Open.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.12,1:34:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.89,1:34:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.13,1:34:26.04,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,These are the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.03,1:34:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They are in there and they didn't crack.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.54,1:34:32.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All thanks to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.62,1:34:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we make with these today?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.58,1:34:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that. They will break.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.37,1:34:39.65,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Since these are eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.64,1:34:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Since these are eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.12,1:34:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.20,1:34:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cracking the eggs for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.90,1:34:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.77,1:34:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Made omurice with the eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.65,1:34:52.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.92,1:34:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.35,1:35:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, the eggs you bought are delicious. They really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.55,1:35:07.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's nice. But Yumemi isn't putting the eggs in her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.39,1:35:07.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.92,1:35:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say aah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.92,1:35:09.88,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,No go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.87,1:35:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.62,1:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.62,1:35:14.04,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama can have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.53,1:35:17.57,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I want mama to enjoy it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.09,1:35:21.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since she purchased it just for mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.29,1:35:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Todays noon nap. I wonder if she's \Ntalking to the old man in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.08,1:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.45,1:35:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she? I've never seen a 2 year old like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.87,1:35:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who cried was the mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.09,1:35:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The bye bye scene with the old man too. \NThe way he stepped back.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.96,1:35:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,First time seeing an old guy doing the moonwalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.58,1:35:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Old guy moonwalk?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.13,1:35:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A 2 year 2 month year old who can talk this well while she can hardly descend stairs
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.81,1:36:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,both the mom and Yumemi are remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.16,1:36:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.00,1:36:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The "open" reveal was amazing as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.33,1:36:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a magic show. Open. So cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.59,1:36:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about the eggs after all that hugging.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.78,1:36:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.77,1:36:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was going like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.77,1:36:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the "sorry for keeping you waiting".
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.96,1:36:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying "sorry for keeping you waiting" and "open" such precious grown up words.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.00,1:36:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.54,1:36:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama how are you feeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:40.09,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.091,106.727)\fs20}Sugiyamas kid will go on an errand now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.00,1:36:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching the previous segments they are all full of drama
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.44,1:36:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but after my son came back I kept asking how it was but he didn't tell me much.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.69,1:36:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so it will be my first time seeing it today.\N I wonder how it will be.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.02,1:36:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Excited? \N- Excited?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.07,1:36:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.41,1:36:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama mama please introduce the clip.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.43,1:37:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my son did his best. \NPlease enjoy this clip.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.81,1:37:08.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ai Sugiyama who reached the world No. 1 in women's doubles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.39,1:37:08.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,No. 1 in the world is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.24,1:37:13.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She won 3 grand slams in the doubles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.95,1:37:12.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.48,1:37:18.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having reached the No. 1 ranking she is called The Super Woman by the tennis world.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.18,1:37:25.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She had 62 consecutive Grand Slam main draw appearances which won her a guiness record.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.15,1:37:31.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In 2009 she retired from her 17 year old tennis career.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.74,1:37:34.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her husband is a former pro-golfer.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.24,1:37:38.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though he is Japanese he was born and raised in Kenya.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.29,1:37:41.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now he's Ai's manager.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.20,1:37:45.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here is Yuu who is 3 years and 8 months old and who loves to play with balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.98,1:37:49.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wonder which one of the parents he is taking after?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.33,1:37:54.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's first see him play golf with his father.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.27,1:37:59.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is he a golfer?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.53,1:38:00.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.75,1:38:03.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or is he a tennis player?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.06,1:38:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.10,1:38:09.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has his game face on.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.66,1:38:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next is mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.52,1:38:15.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ai's tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.07,1:38:22.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It only felt naturally to have the errand\N be centered around this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.88,1:38:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286.546,552.91)\fs27}Sugiyamas 3 rules to bringing up a kid
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.84,1:38:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We want him to always face challenges.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.32,1:38:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first step to accomplish things so that's why we put stress on seriously faces challenges.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.90,1:38:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is not putting limits to their ability \N if I keep telling them that they can't do X thing
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.73,1:38:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that will really destroy the will of my child so instead I will tell them that I believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.08,1:38:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last one is as expected: Waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.08,1:38:55.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those are some splendid rules but some rules are meant to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.39,1:38:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.62,1:39:00.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Like making him eat without waiting after saying "Hurry up and eat".
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.18,1:39:02.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is a big gap between reality and the ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.47,1:39:08.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at the club they make him help them out such as picking up balls on the court.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.57,1:39:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are almost done. Once you are done come to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.53,1:39:14.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not putting limits on their ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.04,1:39:16.36,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,I will be exhausted if I do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.35,1:39:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You will but you are almost done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.55,1:39:21.12,BlueFill,,0,0,0,,I wanna do it with mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.11,1:39:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay but only 3 balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.04,1:39:27.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hasn't she just been made to pick up balls by her son?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.91,1:39:28.93,Studio,,0,0,0,,What was the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.85,1:39:30.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuu easily got away with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.42,1:39:35.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad has a theory on why it's hard to accomplish the ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.14,1:39:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gap between what he is being told and what he wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.87,1:39:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But it takes time to realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.08,1:39:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am the one who is best put together.\N- No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.00,1:39:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.60,1:40:00.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They cuddle him while being being afraid of breaking his back.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.71,1:40:05.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The mom has thought of a plan \Nto make him want to go on an errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.88,1:40:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we directly ask him to do it tomorrow he probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.20,1:40:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about having him do warm ups but we need to give him the resolution to accomplish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.64,1:40:19.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With resolution is how you greet the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.76,1:40:21.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,{\pos(416,608.182)}Will it be fine?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.65,1:40:23.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is dad missing the resolution?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.16,1:40:25.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm crying now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.16,1:40:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of tears are those?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.25,1:40:28.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,He cries so easily.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.20,1:40:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.86,1:40:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's the best put together of the two. Ai seems to be the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.42,1:40:40.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's finally the day of the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.43,1:40:43.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have made him help out extra for a month.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.88,1:40:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good morning. \N- Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.32,1:40:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still dirty over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.54,1:40:49.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.56,1:40:54.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One whole month of this kind of exchange. \NHe must be ready to prove himself helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.35,1:40:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.16,1:40:58.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He enjoys being praised.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.14,1:41:00.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He's so determend. \N - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.24,1:41:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.24,1:41:02.29,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.28,1:41:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It's become really clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.18,1:41:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The balls are all over the 4th tennis court if you could...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.83,1:41:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go after putting the brooms back.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.05,1:41:16.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hurrying to the fourth court.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.27,1:41:17.96,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Nice. \N- Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.88,1:41:21.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The face of a working man.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.48,1:41:26.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not pretending to help but actually being helpful.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.81,1:41:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.44,1:41:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.65,1:41:35.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I did it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.99,1:41:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. You helped out everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.99,1:41:40.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.65,1:41:48.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has come to appreciate helping others out. \N He's ready since the cherry blossom has bloomed at the club.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.04,1:41:56.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have a cherry blossom viewing party every year. \NAnd this year they have a special cake to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.60,1:42:00.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with this cake the errand begins.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.79,1:42:02.27,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.26,1:42:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A racket?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.40,1:42:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember it, Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.43,1:42:07.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The racket is made from chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.58,1:42:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it is!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.58,1:42:12.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Same racket that mom used to play with.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.04,1:42:16.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the same type of racket that Ai was using as a player.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.04,1:42:22.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She sent the racket to the cakemaker \Nand they created a replica.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.75,1:42:28.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the father left the racket at the cake shop on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.73,1:42:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the racket?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.45,1:42:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The racket? Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.00,1:42:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, the real racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.93,1:42:37.63,Studio,,0,0,0,,{\pos(213.273,79.091)}The theatrics have begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.11,1:42:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mistakenly left it at the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.76,1:42:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying that he forgot it. This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.78,1:42:47.55,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Without it you can't play tennis.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.54,1:42:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right. This is no good. \N - We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.46,1:42:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.40,1:42:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging of you. Can you bring it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.79,1:42:58.23,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will? All by myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.22,1:43:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.05,1:43:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if it's lost? It's my most precious racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.58,1:43:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I used it when I was a player.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.95,1:43:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.95,1:43:11.75,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Will I go all by myself? But that's a first.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.74,1:43:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.13,1:43:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.13,1:43:16.91,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.90,1:43:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleepy? So for the party...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.90,1:43:20.85,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.84,1:43:22.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Being sleepy is an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.50,1:43:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's check if it's cold outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.89,1:43:28.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His father is taking him outside.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.51,1:43:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Come. Tell me if it's cold or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.70,1:43:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As your mom said you will become energetic from walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.40,1:43:41.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The dad's reasoning removed the excuse about being sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.42,1:43:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this racket once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.22,1:43:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This means a lot to your mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.48,1:43:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Remember it, Yuu. \N - I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.25,1:43:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.94,1:43:54.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to go with mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.35,1:44:00.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"I want to go with mom". That's not an excuse. \NHe still struggles to find the willpower.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.14,1:44:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's send you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.36,1:44:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.78,1:44:06.79,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.78,1:44:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.75,1:44:11.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They must seize this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.90,1:44:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Find that energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.40,1:44:17.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has lots of power.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.29,1:44:20.07,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to keep crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.06,1:44:22.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Harvesting the energy from crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.20,1:44:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Try to cry with all your might.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.03,1:44:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a mother who is experienced with tears having to appear before finding the willpower.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.88,1:44:36.17,Studio,,0,0,0,,The mother is just smiling through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.56,1:44:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have to cry then cry but \Nturn that energy into something
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.75,1:44:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and do something with it. That is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.49,1:44:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Ai knows all about finding the willpower.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.27,1:44:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you dislike about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.35,1:44:55.49,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will become a missing child.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.48,1:45:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You will definitely not. Follow the road straight ahead. You don't have to turn even once.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.58,1:45:01.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just has to go straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.80,1:45:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.92,1:45:08.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,When someone yawns then it means that they are sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.52,1:45:11.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.73,1:45:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. When you are nervous you yawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.38,1:45:16.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She thwarted yet another excuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.28,1:45:19.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,What if I become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.44,1:45:21.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.06,1:45:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. I have prepared something\N so you won't get lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.29,1:45:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They've even thought of a way to avoid him from getting lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.37,1:45:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A teddy bear. His name is Daiji (precious).
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.37,1:45:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As a baby he would wrap it in a towel \Nand never ever let it out of his sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.92,1:45:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy will be in trouble without the racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.54,1:45:47.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He tries to avoid going by taking Daiji out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.40,1:45:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it can't be helped. \N Let's cancel the party.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.19,1:45:53.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mothers final measure.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.25,1:45:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. If you can't do it then fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.49,1:46:00.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, his father is in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.84,1:46:03.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,- He's not witnessing any of this. \N - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.39,1:46:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he go? I want him to but...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.79,1:46:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His father also can't find the resolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.52,1:46:11.97,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's close to letting him give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.96,1:46:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will refuse in front of everyone. \N I will tell them that Yuu can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.40,1:46:17.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His mother is resolute that he has to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.32,1:46:18.93,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.92,1:46:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.82,1:46:25.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And at that moment Yuu's crying changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.49,1:46:27.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I will go get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.02,1:46:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.22,1:46:31.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Will we meet again when I come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.98,1:46:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That's a given.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.81,1:46:39.53,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Hug me for 5 minutes and then I will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.52,1:46:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.15,1:46:45.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Something took hold in Yuu's heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.68,1:46:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hug you for 5 minutes so you can gather your strength and decide to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.17,1:47:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, you are mammas child so you can definitely do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.52,1:47:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me when you feel strong enough to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.16,1:47:05.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then wait. (Rule 3)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.21,1:47:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me when you are ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.40,1:47:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.81,1:47:13.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found the willpower.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.39,1:47:15.56,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,, I will go.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.35,1:47:16.66,Studio,,0,0,0,,Remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.65,1:47:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's do our best. \NIf it's you, Yuu, then you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.41,1:47:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take mama's...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.52,1:47:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373.818,433.636)}Can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.24,1:47:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The good luck charm contains his mothers wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.58,1:47:32.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is a special backpack.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.73,1:47:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for rackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.14,1:47:35.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rackets can fit in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.91,1:47:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa attached this special band to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.13,1:47:48.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father thought of this and created it. \N There's a hole at the bottom that the grip can go through.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.03,1:47:51.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to explain this to the cake maker?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.34,1:47:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Ready to go. \NPlease do it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.48,1:48:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go from here or should I follow you to the road?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.15,1:48:07.02,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,If it's Yuu, then I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.07,1:48:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go then.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.82,1:48:07.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.27,1:48:09.83,Studio,,0,0,0,,He suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.18,1:48:15.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's gathered all this energy from crying \N it's almost like he's a different person.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.35,1:48:17.30,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.76,1:48:18.84,Studio,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.24,1:48:21.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's straight forward and downhill.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.53,1:48:24.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He needs to pick up the racket from the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.55,1:48:37.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At the convenience store he was asked to get 2 packs of three-color rice balls as well as a cherry blossom steamed bun.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.22,1:48:41.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuu likes to be seen by people and held in esteem.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.98,1:48:48.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But today he is all alone which is hard for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.62,1:48:56.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this moment someone who is always watching Yuu, believes that he can accomplish this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.49,1:48:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amazing. \N- What is?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.95,1:49:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never do this errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.59,1:49:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course you could. \N- I see but...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.31,1:49:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whose kid do you think it is? It's my kid. \N - Hey, make some room for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.82,1:49:13.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Did he feel their confidence in him? \N Yuu started running.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.96,1:49:17.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Right, heading towards the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.74,1:49:25.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Erm wait!? There's a convenience store on the way there? Actually there are 3 right around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.87,1:49:33.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The blossom viewing party basket is in the 100 yen convenience store not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.35,1:49:41.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The things he was asked to get \N I bet they aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.00,1:49:47.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A pink steamed bun as requested?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.24,1:49:49.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Found it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.24,1:49:49.78,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.77,1:49:54.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a thank you "Heisei era for being over" bun.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.70,1:49:54.28,Studio,,0,0,0,,Not it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.27,1:49:57.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No three-colored rice balls \Nbut he picked up mitarashi rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.40,1:50:01.96,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please and thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.95,1:50:05.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately both of them are off.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.11,1:50:06.80,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are close enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.32,1:50:09.82,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Today it's a cherry blossom viewing party.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.81,1:50:12.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His first conversation on the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.22,1:50:15.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Because of the party I had to come alone today.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.56,1:50:15.99,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing, he can converse.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.98,1:50:17.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.31,1:50:21.33,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It's my first time coming out like this alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.77,1:50:23.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Properly paying.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.24,1:50:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From 1000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.37,1:50:32.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And getting the money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.38,1:50:38.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,He was living in Chigasaki prefecture and he's coming home today
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.38,1:50:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He is?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.19,1:50:40.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.16,1:50:42.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's the usual Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.12,1:50:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chigasaki is in Japan, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.00,1:50:49.81,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Since I will become a young boy...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.80,1:50:56.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was a kindergarten entrance ceremony​ \N and he's proud to be considered a young boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.82,1:51:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.73,1:51:03.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No good. He forgot just like his dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.95,1:51:05.24,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.64,1:51:10.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He bought the wrong things but he feels accomplished now.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.30,1:51:13.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He can do things even if people aren't watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.87,1:51:16.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nah, they were watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.18,1:51:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.24,1:51:23.49,Studio,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.45,1:51:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's split it.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.45,1:51:26.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,They are sharing it!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.42,1:51:29.37,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's up with this comedy duo.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.84,1:51:30.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From their expensive apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.68,1:51:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see. Can you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.03,1:51:34.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are watching over him.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.73,1:51:34.64,Studio,,0,0,0,,Such a good relation.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.86,1:51:36.76,Studio,,0,0,0,,That was funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.39,1:51:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Peew.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.97,1:51:42.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.04,1:51:44.42,Studio,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Daiji.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.20,1:51:48.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Daiji (precious) the teddy bear.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.09,1:51:55.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He dropped Daiji and ran off and as an exception the staff called out to him about Daiji.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.18,1:51:53.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,He didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.95,1:52:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous running so close to the road and you seem to have dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.28,1:52:04.13,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.12,1:52:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that brown thing not yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.50,1:52:10.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daiji isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.33,1:52:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It fell off from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.42,1:52:17.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Daiji was with him when he learned to walk and of course they always slept together.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.48,1:52:22.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And when he rides a car or when they went to France he can go anywhere as long as Daiji is with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.90,1:52:27.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This 6th generation Daiji who is a bit dirty.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.13,1:52:28.05,Studio,,0,0,0,,- 6th generation. \N- That much?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.02,1:52:31.45,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Never leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.79,1:52:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,216.909)\fs50\frz323.9}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.36,1:52:56.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's exhausted from going down the hill. For those times...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.19,1:52:58.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Energy injection.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.73,1:53:01.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's candy for revitalizing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.48,1:53:01.31,Studio,,0,0,0,,Candy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.30,1:53:07.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Please eat it when you feel exhausted" his mother said and put it in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.32,1:53:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's walking again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.09,1:53:12.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuu who came to a sudden stop started walking again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.89,1:53:14.90,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.06,1:53:19.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.00,1:53:25.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As part of the Swiss owned hotel \Nhere they make their own original cakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.99,1:53:25.72,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks so yummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.71,1:53:29.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He came to pick up the racket his father forgot there.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.79,1:53:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.48,1:53:35.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The owner and chef.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.37,1:53:37.38,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please give me a racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.37,1:53:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A racket?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.04,1:53:42.01,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama used to play tennis.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.00,1:53:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama's racket? I will go look for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.97,1:53:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be inside the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.16,1:53:50.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.76,1:53:55.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The chef understood it too \Nthat this is an important racket
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.13,1:53:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the one?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.86,1:54:00.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's making sure that this is mamas racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.29,1:54:04.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Not like many people forget rackets in this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.65,1:54:06.71,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please put it in this red bag for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.70,1:54:10.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Explaining this will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.83,1:54:10.32,Studio,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.59,1:54:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This one? Will it fit?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.74,1:54:13.89,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.88,1:54:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bigger than the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:15.37,1:54:21.39,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Not this end. From here. \N There's a hole down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.79,1:54:19.77,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.38,1:54:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there is a hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.84,1:54:23.22,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.23,1:54:25.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And put it through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.73,1:54:29.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was able to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.94,1:54:29.52,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.51,1:54:35.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,And then put it through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.69,1:54:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.69,1:54:38.09,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,You're sweating.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.08,1:54:41.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chef, we appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.60,1:54:41.78,Studio,,0,0,0,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.77,1:54:43.59,Studio,,0,0,0,,Cause he's using all his effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.58,1:54:47.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The chef is using all his skill.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.76,1:54:49.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Chef! \N- Chef, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.29,1:54:51.52,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.51,1:54:52.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.77,1:54:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try it out?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.23,1:54:56.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.78,1:54:59.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.78,1:54:59.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.13,1:55:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, take it back to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.78,1:55:08.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mothers important racket and the groceries.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.66,1:55:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.54,1:55:12.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, chef.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.76,1:55:21.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 100 yen convinience store where the requested items are on the other side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.05,1:55:24.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's very close to where he's walking right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.81,1:55:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he got the racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.43,1:55:30.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They can't see well from this angle.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.76,1:55:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.11,1:55:40.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even if no one is watching over him\NYuu is doing just fine, mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:41.54,1:55:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- He finally went out. \N- He did.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.23,1:55:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- How has it been so far? \N- It really took a while to get him to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.19,1:55:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried if he would be fine but gradually his behavior changed so I started having confidence in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.03,1:55:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It changed the moment he left.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.61,1:56:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I was surprised by that change.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.63,1:56:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understand the strength of your son\Nbut I also understood the weakness of your husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.15,1:56:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.82,1:56:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so anxious the day before.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.08,1:56:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even he didn't understood why he was crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.93,1:56:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even said that he couldn't do the errand.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.05,1:56:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,About this teary-eyed father\N he is in fact in the studio today
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.64,1:56:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu's papa, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.24,1:56:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.52,1:56:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you came all the way, \Nwhy don't you come and sit here with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.31,1:56:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, everybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.37,1:56:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.57,1:56:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From "my first errand" to "my first trial".
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.17,1:56:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The father is on trial now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.07,1:56:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.48,1:56:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032.727,539.818)}Just finished wailing.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.66,1:56:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, please share how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.10,1:56:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find the words.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.42,1:56:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mama is so strong. \N- She is.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.90,1:57:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like she said. If I was alone in this I would immediately give in and go with him to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.43,1:57:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mostly cut out but I was in that car for long mumbling "isn't it enough already".
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.42,1:57:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept thinking about giving up but \NAi said that this kid can definitely do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:17.87,1:57:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her confidence in our son was so strong that it started rubbing off on me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.63,1:57:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the strength of a mother. \N- What a cool mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.65,1:57:30.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's time to go shopping again.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.51,1:57:37.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He needs to get 2 packs of three-color rice balls as well as a cherry blossom steamed bun. Then back to the tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.98,1:57:41.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since he doesn't have to hold the racket he can raise his hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.60,1:57:44.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The father really thought of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.39,1:57:47.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Isn't the camera too close?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.51,1:57:51.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.84,1:57:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932.364,320.182)}Camera
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.03,1:57:58.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.64,1:58:02.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For those times...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.04,1:58:01.60,Studio,,0,0,0,,Suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.59,1:58:03.92,Studio,,0,0,0,,Too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.91,1:58:09.62,Studio,,0,0,0,,Weird. No one behaves like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.61,1:58:16.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Why is he playing tennis here?" \Nhe wonders but he didn't notice the camera.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.89,1:58:16.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.70,1:58:18.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.22,1:58:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu, take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.42,1:58:24.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The chef was watching over him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.07,1:58:25.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:25.35,1:58:30.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected, he does best when people watch over him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.52,1:58:37.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has arrived at the 100 yen store.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.96,1:58:44.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cherry blossom viewing party basket is right near the entrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.35,1:58:46.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.74,1:58:53.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He found the rice balls and was asked to get two.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.17,1:58:56.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Remarkable. \N- He knows to get two.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:57.90,1:59:02.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Here's another one for Yuu to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.12,1:59:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,296 yen, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:05.67,1:59:12.12,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,We are having a party. Mama, Yuu and papa will eat this.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.97,1:59:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is this an important racket?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.09,1:59:19.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the racket that accomplished the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.51,1:59:20.55,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.64,1:59:23.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,My mom used to be a tennis player
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.73,1:59:26.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,back then she used this racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.40,1:59:31.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of all people, this is Sugiyama Ai's racket.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.15,1:59:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of player was your mother? \NWas she a great player?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.40,1:59:37.03,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes, she lost to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.40,1:59:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(612.363,68.546)\fs32}TN: He mistakes the preposition. \NTiny mistake but results in the opposite meaning.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.68,1:59:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's pretty wrong. \N - It's the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.42,1:59:43.41,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,She would lose to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.40,1:59:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't lose to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.35,1:59:48.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Don't forget like your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.80,1:59:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,, Don't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.65,1:59:54.69,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.65,1:59:54.69,Studio,,0,0,0,,Looks heavy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.68,2:00:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he's there. Isn't that Yuu?\NIt is. Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.35,2:00:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's carrying something.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.60,2:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't see. \N- I want to see. I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.12,2:00:09.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's begging.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.02,2:00:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright, have a look. \N- Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.17,2:00:16.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What they can't see is his expression.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.04,2:00:19.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And of course they can't see what he bought either.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.47,2:00:23.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He accomplished everything he was asked to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.66,2:00:26.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's entering the convenience store again.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.05,2:00:28.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He already has all he needs.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.96,2:00:31.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is he going to purchase?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.83,2:00:40.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He picked up the racket and purchased all that's needed so why did he go into a third convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.03,2:00:42.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is he getting?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.20,2:00:44.35,Studio,,0,0,0,,He really loves stores.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.73,2:00:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.59,2:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't carry all that, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.12,2:00:54.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They could see he was carrying a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.59,2:01:00.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are no needed items.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.01,2:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come home.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:05.82,2:01:09.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to get.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.08,2:01:11.14,Studio,,0,0,0,,What will he purchase?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.13,2:01:13.99,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where is Pamu?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.98,2:01:16.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Pamu is the name of the tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.91,2:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Pamu?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.91,2:01:20.18,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I just want to go back to Pamu.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.16,2:01:27.11,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I want to go back there since I was running an errand and now I want to return.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.10,2:01:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pamu isn't the name of a house so what is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.84,2:01:35.08,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,In a court you go like this.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.61,2:01:37.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.61,2:01:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A tennis court?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.93,2:01:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have to go up the hill. \NCan you go up there?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.92,2:01:44.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:42.92,2:01:44.59,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.42,2:01:49.36,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.42,2:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.53,2:01:49.36,Studio,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.35,2:01:54.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He knew the way, of course. \NHe just wanted to talk.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.48,2:01:55.21,Studio,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.20,2:01:58.11,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Alright. I will go.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.17,2:02:24.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His resolute expression is different from his crying face.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.02,2:02:28.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But this power was born from his crying.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.73,2:02:32.38,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Mama must be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.33,2:02:39.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mama's world No. 1 has been entrusted to Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.52,2:02:41.65,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,This is so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.20,2:02:49.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yuu is back at the tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.83,2:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.86,2:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.86,2:02:57.17,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,I purchased this.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.16,2:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you buy? And my racket? \NThank you, it's my important racket.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.84,2:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's perfect. \N- Amazing. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.05,2:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.78,2:03:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you manage to ask for it?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:14.62,2:03:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- At the cake shop? \N- Did you ask the cake maker?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.88,2:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,From happiness since you did so well. I think you are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.88,2:03:23.48,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Why are there tears coming out?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.41,2:03:26.05,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Where's the cake?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.69,2:03:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- First show us what you bought. \N- Tell us, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.01,2:03:34.14,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,The chef gave me...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.13,2:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, mama loves those.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.13,2:03:38.37,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,These things.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.36,2:03:45.18,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,That's right mama. I thought mama loves these so...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.17,2:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I love mitarashi rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.40,2:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.51,2:03:53.94,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,It was fun on my first errand.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.93,2:03:58.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was happy to do it in the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.08,2:04:00.70,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Please eat this.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.84,2:04:04.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Time for the cherry blossom viewing party.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.83,2:04:04.82,Studio,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.84,2:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu did his best for the party. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.54,2:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did his best.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.74,2:04:15.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nice smile.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.09,2:04:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.25,2:04:21.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was asked to get them but these are mama's beloved mitarashi rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.96,2:04:23.74,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Not that good.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.58,2:04:25.40,Studio,,0,0,0,,Not that good?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:24.75,2:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Super tasty.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.36,2:04:31.57,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Everyone, be careful that it doesn't get caught in your throats
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.56,2:04:34.44,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,so please eat it slowly
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.15,2:04:36.02,Studio,,0,0,0,,He's worried about them.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.36,2:04:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yuu, what do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.47,2:04:41.97,WhiteBlueBorder,,0,0,0,,Cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.58,2:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chef?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:44.67,2:04:47.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Neither golf nor tennis
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.55,2:04:52.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but Yuu might become the worlds best chef.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:57.30,2:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Splendid. \N - It was splendid.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.15,2:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got them because mama loves them.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.24,2:05:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That tugged at my heartstrings.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:03.20,2:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at first I thought that we should get rice balls matching the color of cherry blossom
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.18,2:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but normally I go for mitarashi rice balls and usually go for them so he must've been observing me.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:18.63,2:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- I totally thought he had made a mistake. \N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.24,2:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was to show gratitude towards his mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.39,2:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you okay after watching this?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.58,2:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(756.364,615.455)\fs28}Too much crying.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.21,2:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm lost for words.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.20,2:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you okay? \N- Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.10,2:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying throughout.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.51,2:05:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And one staff member had a camera in his racket. What was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.32,2:05:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who holds a racket like this?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.86,2:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cute kid. And just like how we watched a mother raising their boy this time we have a 4 year old girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.85,2:06:02.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Inami in Toyama prefecture is a \Nflourishing town built around a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.36,2:06:11.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wood crafting is famous there and many sculptures around.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.48,2:06:10.90,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.36,2:06:15.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And there we find a bustling road leading up to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.03,2:06:18.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this kimono fabrics store we find a 4 year old girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.00,2:06:22.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here is Sae who helps out her mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.78,2:06:22.04,Studio,,0,0,0,,Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.03,2:06:24.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She does everything in earnestness.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.62,2:06:30.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She loves working at the shop and \Nshe also helps out her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.02,2:06:38.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Readying the spare change. Grandma brings them every day this to a supermarket close by.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.03,2:06:40.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Putting the change in a bag.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.97,2:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking off.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:40.97,2:06:44.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.90,2:06:48.91,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Make sure to work hard and come back.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.62,2:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(749.091,443.818)}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.41,2:06:52.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Grandma has been out for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.94,2:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.12,2:06:55.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A call from her.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.99,2:06:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Sae, she's saying that she forgot the money.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.98,2:07:01.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The 50 yen coin bag.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:01.32,2:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.19,2:07:04.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The grandmas strategy.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.56,2:07:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.97,2:07:08.82,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.81,2:07:10.53,Studio,,0,0,0,,They hid it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.78,2:07:10.97,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.96,2:07:13.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae is full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.99,2:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Sae?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.48,2:07:17.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that she will go on an errand?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.67,2:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it underneath it??
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.78,2:07:24.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae, can you bring this? To Asamo.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.28,2:07:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.28,2:07:25.70,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.69,2:07:27.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.52,2:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers for Buddha have withered. Can you also get some fresh ones?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.36,2:07:34.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.44,2:07:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The town next door is after the big crossing\Ngrandma's shop is in the supermarket
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.84,2:07:44.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she can buy the flowers in the same building.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.62,2:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:44.62,2:07:49.34,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.33,2:07:53.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae, has been begging to go on \Nan errand so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.64,2:07:56.52,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.64,2:07:56.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,32.181)\fs24}TN: Ending a sentence in dawa is very lady like and cute.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.51,2:07:58.19,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,So fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.45,2:07:59.08,Studio,,0,0,0,,So fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.18,2:08:04.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is her first errand and it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.22,2:08:15.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has arrived at the crossing and this sculpture has been made in Inami.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.94,2:08:19.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Inami.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.06,2:08:21.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It can talk.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.47,2:08:24.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From here on the scenery immediately changes.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.53,2:08:30.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A wide crossing with no obstructed view\N and since few cars pass there are no traffic lights.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.54,2:08:33.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She always crosses with her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.03,2:08:41.27,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Right, left, right.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.26,2:08:48.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae never looked back once. \NShe looks and walks forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.97,2:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she crossed.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.62,2:09:00.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She crossed it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.27,2:09:04.91,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.90,2:09:08.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae broke a good sweat.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.95,2:09:18.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has a towel in her right for wiping her sweat \Nin her left pocket she has a towel for tears.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.48,2:09:22.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What are the carving today? \N A dragon or a daruma?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.62,2:09:27.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She considered asking them \Nbut she can't today.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:27.45,2:09:37.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I have to go to Asumo I can't do other things.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.40,2:09:40.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pink roof is where she is headed.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.83,2:09:44.76,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I finally approached it.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.62,2:09:50.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like mother said, if you go\N straight then it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.45,2:09:56.18,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I can go by myself. How great. I'm a genius.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.17,2:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A genius.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.32,2:10:04.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's cool. Always great with air condition.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.52,2:10:07.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is her grandmothers shop.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.59,2:10:12.98,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Grandma, I brought you the things you forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.97,2:10:15.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She gave it her all just for her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.79,2:10:18.41,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It was beneath the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.40,2:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. I was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.82,2:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.55,2:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's all there. Thank you for bringing it here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.24,2:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.24,2:10:31.02,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will get flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.01,2:10:34.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In fact, a monk will come visit grandpa house.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.78,2:10:37.29,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.28,2:10:39.58,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I came by myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.57,2:10:46.10,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Uwa, so many beatiful flowers. \N I'm completely at loss.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.09,2:10:53.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Flowers for buddha, they are all made to be similar but it seems like she's found the best one.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.51,2:10:55.52,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,These are cute.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.90,2:10:58.68,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Flowers for buddha, I will go home with these.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:58.67,2:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.12,2:11:04.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her important purse given to her by grandma.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.81,2:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,380 yen please.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.30,2:11:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has two 500 yen coins in her wallet.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.43,2:11:15.20,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Since I'm just a kid I don't know if this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.84,2:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one 500 yen coin please.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.71,2:11:23.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She always handles the loose change \Nbut today is her first time paying.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.27,2:11:28.62,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.27,2:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:31.74,2:11:35.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, it was cool inside.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.56,2:11:41.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's April and the Hokuriku regions' summer has begun.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.56,2:11:43.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.77,2:11:48.16,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's become hotter than before.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:54.86,2:11:58.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Clank clank clank sounds can be heard.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:58.21,2:12:00.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She's almost home.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.39,2:12:02.92,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:00.39,2:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot today.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:04.67,2:12:10.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone watches over her \Nand that's why she can do her best.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.27,2:12:14.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This town raises and holds children dear.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.25,2:12:19.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's been going on for years \Nand is now part of normal life in Inami.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.81,2:12:23.22,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.48,2:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.87,2:12:26.50,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I was able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.74,2:12:28.58,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I was able to go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.57,2:12:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You are remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:30.40,2:12:32.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:32.25,2:12:37.14,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,On my way back it was way hotter than the way over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.13,2:12:38.86,Studio,,0,0,0,,She's sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.07,2:12:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.84,2:12:40.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:40.47,2:12:42.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:43.05,2:12:47.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which is why the mother conceived a second errand.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.76,2:12:58.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She will go visit the temple to call the monk over to their home so that she can pray at their home altar.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.04,2:13:05.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are many temples in Inami so her mother is trying to give her clear directions.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.10,2:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go this way, on the right side there is a spinning blue and red thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:14.16,2:13:17.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a spinning barber's pole.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.01,2:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With it to your back you will have the temple in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.32,2:13:23.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Butsugon temple.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.55,2:13:27.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.55,2:13:27.59,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.05,2:13:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.09,2:13:33.86,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good, gooooood.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.21,2:13:33.39,Studio,,0,0,0,,Nice smile.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.63,2:13:36.15,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I will head off.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.14,2:13:41.04,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,My life is so full of errands.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.00,2:14:02.71,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,My life is so full of errands.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.15,2:14:03.98,Studio,,0,0,0,,What's up with this song.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.34,2:14:11.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This isn't her first errand, it's her second. \NShe's looking for the spinning barber's pole.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.55,2:14:18.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Spinning spinning, where are you? Spinning.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.51,2:14:24.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's there. Seems like it's their day off.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.02,2:14:26.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She passed it by.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.69,2:14:28.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,Was hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.12,2:14:31.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And that's right this is the temple.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.87,2:14:36.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cameraman races ahead of her.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:36.76,2:14:38.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wait, she stopped.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.36,2:14:43.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She turned back.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:45.12,2:14:55.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's odd. Her mother mentioned this spinning pole but it's quite inconspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.81,2:15:00.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Why can't this errand veteran see it?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.06,2:15:04.30,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mother, it wasn't spinning at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.55,2:15:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it isn't spinning that's the right one.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:08.55,2:15:10.96,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I stood with it to my back.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.95,2:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a temple?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.28,2:15:19.54,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,There was but there are temples here and there so I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.53,2:15:21.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She really gave it her all.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:20.73,2:15:23.19,Studio,,0,0,0,,Cause that's what kind of town it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.18,2:15:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.62,2:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put this on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.84,2:15:32.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She put a glittering bracelet on her right hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.73,2:15:35.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do this and it's the temple on the left.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.24,2:15:37.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To the right of the spinning pole.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.30,2:15:39.81,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.30,2:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.80,2:15:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see it though it wasn't spinning?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:43.52,2:15:45.97,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It wasn't spinning.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:45.96,2:15:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would but it's their day off today. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.88,2:15:53.70,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Mother, you were slightly bad.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.20,2:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.28,2:15:58.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This errands veteran is ready to departure.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.00,2:16:01.95,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've understood.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.00,2:16:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "excuse me" in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.44,2:16:04.63,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.44,2:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You will fall if you run.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:10.30,2:16:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can do it if she understands what. That's Sae's good point. But she is getting tired. This is her second errand today after all.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.77,2:16:19.75,Studio,,0,0,0,,And it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:20.33,2:16:23.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright, she has arrived in front of the pole.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.73,2:16:26.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's fine even if it doesn't spin.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:27.21,2:16:34.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With it to your back there is a temple on the right and one on the left. Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:31.14,2:16:33.81,Studio,,0,0,0,,- So that's what it was. \N- That's hard to discern.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.28,2:16:38.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,According to the bracelet that her mother put on her.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.93,2:16:41.11,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.10,2:16:47.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. The temple on the right. The Butsugon temple.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:46.56,2:16:48.68,Studio,,0,0,0,,Glad she got it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.46,2:16:53.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is her first time alone at a temple.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:51.74,2:16:55.71,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Scary to be alone at a temple. \N- It is scary.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.74,2:16:59.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Straight to the main building.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.63,2:17:08.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,One step at a time. The talkative Sae is really quiet right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.56,2:17:14.37,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.36,2:17:17.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She calls out with a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.20,2:17:23.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No one comes out.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:24.29,2:17:27.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She won't cry. She won't be perturbed.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.45,2:17:28.97,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.09,2:17:33.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She calls out in an even louder voice this time.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.31,2:17:37.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But no one comes out.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.26,2:17:37.33,Studio,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.95,2:17:47.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There's also a building over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.90,2:17:53.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is the building where the monk lives which is also called Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:53.55,2:17:55.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The door is open.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.47,2:18:02.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she goes inside and calls out loudly then the monk will come out but she doesn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:02.75,2:18:06.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She can't bring herself forward.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:06.88,2:18:10.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's dark inside and smells heavily of incense.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.43,2:18:17.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Since this is the way she better\N fight through the scary feeling.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.92,2:18:23.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bracelet her mother gave her is her only support.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.52,2:18:26.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will head in. At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:31.41,2:18:35.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will head in. At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.69,2:18:43.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bracelet broke.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.86,2:18:50.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She picks up the beads but she can't fix it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.68,2:18:57.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae, is this all too much?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:00.62,2:19:08.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She won't go home. These are all new \Nexperiences for the 4 year old Sae.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.43,2:19:11.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then this expression.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.12,2:19:25.06,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.65,2:19:29.46,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.94,2:19:32.74,Studio,,0,0,0,,Thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.50,2:19:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:35.56,2:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.90,2:19:40.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From within the dark someone approaches.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:40.00,2:19:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Sae?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:41.63,2:19:42.29,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.28,2:19:45.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But it's a familiar face.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.08,2:19:48.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is the monk.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.48,2:19:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:51.23,2:19:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.60,2:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will receive this.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.60,2:19:54.48,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.47,2:19:56.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a gift for Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.73,2:20:05.00,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I called you but you were a bit slow so I was wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:05.21,2:20:07.25,Studio,,0,0,0,,- Slow? \N- She was slow.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:07.69,2:20:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for being slow.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.60,2:20:11.68,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:11.67,2:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it? I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.42,2:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go right away.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:16.75,2:20:19.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This errand was a success.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.16,2:20:26.60,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I was on so many errands today. \NI came to visit Buddha and I...
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.59,2:20:30.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The words burst out of her in one go.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:31.68,2:20:37.99,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Yesterday I went to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.98,2:20:41.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which ocean? I forgot that.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.86,2:20:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgo..
Dialogue: 0,2:20:42.60,2:20:45.88,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,My father played soooo much with me.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.87,2:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.38,2:20:54.53,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,My little brother was with me. \NAnd mother. We were four all in all.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.40,2:20:59.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now we all know what Sae has been doing all week.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.57,2:21:04.45,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:04.51,2:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sae, did you do your best?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.30,2:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.24,2:21:13.31,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I chose pink carnations.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.30,2:21:16.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Flowers from her first errand.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.26,2:21:21.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monk from the second errand.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.99,2:21:27.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Breaking a sweat from all the hard work and deep in prayer, her grandpa would be proud.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.96,2:21:35.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Having fought through two errands \N she now fights off sleepiness.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:40.22,2:21:44.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This was Sae who loves giving her all.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.40,2:21:45.20,Studio,,0,0,0,,She really did.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.32,2:21:53.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,11 years later.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.32,2:21:57.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The place we are meeting with Sae...
Dialogue: 0,2:21:57.43,2:22:01.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Is this an outdoor stage? No no.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.85,2:22:07.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The girl wearing the aqua green is climbing the wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:08.11,2:22:10.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's Sae.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.76,2:22:17.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sae who still loves to give it her all is now in 3rd year of middle school where she's a rock climber.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.14,2:22:21.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In elementary school she came 3rd in her prefecture within the C-class.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:21.55,2:22:24.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In first year of middle school she became the first in B-class in the prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.65,2:22:32.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She also won a second place in another bouldering competition.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.22,2:22:33.13,Studio,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:32.42,2:22:38.41,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And this spring she became number one in her prefecture in the group of young girls.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:38.40,2:22:41.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A little more and she will win in the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.26,2:22:46.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She fell.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.26,2:22:46.51,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,So tough.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:48.31,2:22:55.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She puts chalk on her hands from her bag and goes straight back to it without a break for her muscles.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:55.34,2:22:57.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That was all the break she got.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.67,2:23:00.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking the place she failed as a new challenge.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:00.28,2:23:04.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She grows strong from all the climbing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.16,2:23:07.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time she climbs only using the red stones.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.98,2:23:13.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She has accomplished it when she attaches her rope to the clip above.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.64,2:23:18.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She did it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.41,2:23:20.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please lower me.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:20.97,2:23:26.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We asked Sae about why she becomes so perfectly focused while climbing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.80,2:23:32.72,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I love the feeling after I've accomplished a climb.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.71,2:23:41.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As I become able to climb more difficult ones I become so happy that I just can't stop doing it.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:41.16,2:23:44.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What kind of child has she become?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:45.24,2:23:47.29,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.28,2:23:51.16,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I might not have changed that much after all.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.37,2:23:57.51,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I still love to excel in everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.50,2:24:01.36,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,And I never stopped breaking a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:02.28,2:24:04.18,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:04.18,2:24:07.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Always outperforms on her second try.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:07.53,2:24:10.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now she only climbs on the green stones.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:10.95,2:24:17.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her closest goal is to pass to the National Athletic Meet and perform well there.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:16.08,2:24:17.44,Studio,,0,0,0,,Scary.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.43,2:24:21.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then she hopes to do well at the Junior Olympics.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:22.19,2:24:25.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She also accomplished it in her second try.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:27.44,2:24:29.57,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,Please lower me.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.57,2:24:36.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She does this all by herself. She has developed a splendid view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:36.66,2:24:39.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What does she want to be when she grows up?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.53,2:24:49.11,WhiteVioletBorder,,0,0,0,,I love science so either sports science or nutritional science. That would be a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:49.15,2:24:53.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This was Sae who is radiant from all her hard work.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.39,2:24:55.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,

